  <para style="h">UJobe</para>
  <para style="toc1">UJobe</para>
  <para style="toc2">UJobe</para>
  <para style="toc3">Job</para>
  <para style="mt1">UJobe</para>
  <para style="imt">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="imt1">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="im">Ubuciko beZaga buchaza indlela ukulunga okuthungamelela ngayo ekuphumeleleni. UMtshumayeli ulingisa lokhu, elimukisa ukuthi imvuzo kayikabi khona izikhathi zonke njengoba sokugcwele “ubumenemene” kulumhlaba. Incwadi kaJobe idlulela phambili iveza ukuthi abalungileyo bahlupheka kanjani kwezinye izikhathi. Lincwadi isebenzisa amazwi enhlakanipho ajayelekileyo evela emasikweni endulo: inkulumo eyeluliweyo igxile enkulumeni yobunkondlo.</para>
  <para style="ip">UJobe wethulwe njengendoda elungileyo. Kodwa “omubi” (<char style="tl">satan</char> ngesiHebheru) uveza uhlupho oluyibuqili ngesimilo sikaNkulunkulu sokukhangela umhlaba. Nxa ubuhle buhlezi bulomvuzo, singakwazi kanjani ukuthi kuvela othandweni lukaNkulunkulu kumbe ezifisweni zokubuthelela? Ngakho uNkulunkulu uvumela omubi ukuthi alethe inhlupho empilweni kaJobe.</para>
  <para style="ip">UJobe kamthuki uNkulunkulu njengokucabanga komubi kodwa uphetha esephikisana labangane bakhe abathathu, u-Elifazi, uBhilidadi loZofa. Imibono yabo yemvelo yomhlaba engaqhakazekanga ibenza bakholwe ukuthi ukona kukaJobe yikho okwenza ahlupheke. Ekuphetheni kwendaba kungena ijaha elibizwa ngokuthi ngu-Elihu ikanti uJobe uqhubeka egcizelela ukuthi konanga lutho ngakho kumele athonisiswe phambi kukaNkulunkulu.</para>
  <para style="ip">Ekucineni uNkulunkulu uveza amandla lenhlakanipho ebonakala endalweni. UJobe uvuma ngokuzehlisa ekungaqedisisini kwakhe. Lapho uNkulunkulu esethulise abangane bakaJobe bobathathu, sibona belomlandu odlula abebewunika uJobe. Isiphetho uNkulunkulu ubusisa uJobe ngokuphindwe kabili kulokhu abelakho. Lincwadi isilimukisa ukuthi singalokothi seyise isimilo sokubusa kukaNkulunkulu sikwenze ubuwula.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="JOB 1"/>
  <para style="s1">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 1:1"/>Elizweni lase-Uzi kwakuhlala indoda eyayithiwa nguJobe. Indoda le yayingelasici, iqotho; yayimesaba uNkulunkulu njalo ikuxwaya okubi. <verse eid="JOB 1:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 1:2"/>Yayilamadodana ayisikhombisa lamadodakazi amathathu, <verse eid="JOB 1:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 1:3"/>ilezimvu eziyizinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa, amakamela azinkulungwane ezintathu, izipani zenkabi ezingamakhulu amahlanu labobabhemi abangamakhulu amahlanu, njalo ilezisebenzi ezinengi. Yayinothile kulabo bonke abantu beMpumalanga.<verse eid="JOB 1:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 1:4"/>Amadodana akhe ayesenza amazopha okwenza amadili okuthakazelela amalanga okuzalwa kwawo ezindlini zawo, anxuse odadewabo bobathathu ukuzakudla anathe labo. <verse eid="JOB 1:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 1:5"/>Kwakusithi mhla idili liphela, uJobe wayewabiza azowahlambulula. Ekuseni kakhulu wayesenza umnikelo wokutshiswa wamunye ngamunye esithi, “Mhlawumbe abantwabami benzile isono bathuka uNkulunkulu ezinhliziyweni zabo.” Lo waba ngumkhuba wakhe uJobe.<verse eid="JOB 1:5"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukulingwa Kokuqala KukaJobe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 1:6"/>Ngelinye ilanga izingilosi zeza ukuzezethula phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>, loSathane weza lazo. <verse eid="JOB 1:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 1:7"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuSathane, “Uvela ngaphi?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="JOB 1:7">USathane wamphendula <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wathi, “Ngivela ekuzulazuleni emhlabeni, ngihambahamba ngisiya le lale.”<verse eid="JOB 1:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 1:8"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuSathane, “Usuke wayinanzelela yini inceku yami uJobe? Kakho emhlabeni onjengaye; kalasici, uqondile, indoda emesabayo uNkulunkulu, exwaya okubi.”<verse eid="JOB 1:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 1:9"/>USathane waphendula wathi, “Kambe uJobe umesaba kungelasizatho na uNkulunkulu? <verse eid="JOB 1:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 1:10"/>Kawumbiyelanga ngothango yini yena lendlu yakhe, kanye lakho konke alakho? Uwubusisile umsebenzi wezandla zakhe kuze kuthi imihlambi yakhe yezimvu leyenkomo igcwale ilizwe lonke. <verse eid="JOB 1:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 1:11"/>Kodwa ake welule isandla sakho uchithe konke alakho, uzabona uzakuthuka ebusweni bakho.”<verse eid="JOB 1:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 1:12"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuSathane, “Kulungile, konke alakho kusezandleni zakho, kodwa yena ngokwakhe ungamthinti.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="JOB 1:12">USathane wasesuka phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>.<verse eid="JOB 1:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 1:13"/>Ngelinye ilanga amadodana kaJobe lamadodakazi akhe ayezitika ngokudla, enatha iwayini endlini yomnewabo omdala, <verse eid="JOB 1:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 1:14"/>isithunywa safika kuJobe sathi, “Inkabi bezilima labobabhemi besidla eduze khonapho, <verse eid="JOB 1:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 1:15"/>kwafika amaSabhini ahlasela aqhuba konke ahamba. Izisebenzi azicakazile ngenkemba kwasala mina ngedwa engisindileyo ukuzakubikela!”<verse eid="JOB 1:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 1:16"/>Sisakhuluma esinye isithunywa safika sathi, “Umlilo kaNkulunkulu wehle uvela ezulwini wazitshisa izimvu lezisebenzi, kusele mina ngedwa engisindileyo ukuzakubikela!”<verse eid="JOB 1:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 1:17"/>Elokhu esakhuluma kwafika esinye isithunywa sathi, “AmaKhaladiya abe ngamaqembu amathathu ehlela emakameleni akho awaqhuba ahamba lawo. Izisebenzi azicakazile ngenkemba kwasila mina ngedwa ukuzakubikela!”<verse eid="JOB 1:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 1:18"/>Elokhu esakhuluma kwafika njalo esinye isithunywa sathi, “Amadodana lamadodakazi akho abesidla edilini enatha iwayini endlini yomnewabo omdala, <verse eid="JOB 1:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 1:19"/>kwathi masinyane vungu isavunguzane siqhamuka enkangala saphekula amagumbi womane endlu. Yathi mbo phezu kwabo bahle bafa, kwasila mina ngedwa ukuzakubikela!”<verse eid="JOB 1:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 1:20"/>Ekuzwa lokho uJobe wasukuma wadabula isembatho sakhe, waphuca ikhanda lakhe. Wazilahla phansi wakhonza <verse eid="JOB 1:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 1:21"/>wathi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 1:21">“Ngaphuma ngize esiswini sikamama,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 1:21">njalo ngizasuka ngize.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 1:21">
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wapha njalo usethethe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 1:21">kalidunyiswe ibizo <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>.”<verse eid="JOB 1:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 1:22"/>Phakathi kwakho konke lokhu uJobe kazange enze isono ngokubeka umlandu wokuthi athi uNkulunkulu wonile.<verse eid="JOB 1:22"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="JOB 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="JOB 2"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukulingwa Kwesibili KukaJobe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 2:1"/>Kwelinye ilanga njalo izingilosi zeza phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>, loSathane laye weza lazo ukuzezethula kuye. <verse eid="JOB 2:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 2:2"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuSathane, “Uvela ngaphi?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="JOB 2:2">USathane wamphendula wathi, “Ngivela ekuzulazuleni emhlabeni, ngihambahamba ngisiya le lale kuwo.”<verse eid="JOB 2:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 2:3"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuSathane, “Usuke wayinanzelela yini inceku yami uJobe? Kakho emhlabeni onjengaye; kalasici, uqondile, indoda emesabayo uNkulunkulu, exwaya okubi. Ulokhu emi kubo ubuqotho bakhe lanxa wangiphoqa ukuthi ngimdilize kungelasizatho.”<verse eid="JOB 2:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 2:4"/>USathane waphendula wathi, “Isikhumba ngesikhumba! Umuntu anganikela loba yini alayo ukusiza impilo yakhe. <verse eid="JOB 2:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 2:5"/>Kodwa yelula isandla sakho umtshaye inyama lamathambo akhe, uzabona uzakuthuka ebusweni bakho.”<verse eid="JOB 2:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 2:6"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuSathane, “Kulungile, usezandleni zakho, kodwa ungayithinti impilo yakhe.”<verse eid="JOB 2:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 2:7"/>Ngakho uSathane wasesuka phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> wathela uJobe izilonda ezibuhlungu kusukela ngaphansi kwezinyawo zakhe kusiyafika esicholo sekhanda lakhe. <verse eid="JOB 2:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 2:8"/>UJobe wasethatha ucezu lodengezi wazihwaya ngalo ehlezi esilotheni.<verse eid="JOB 2:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 2:9"/>Umkakhe wathi kuye, “Ulokhu ubambelele kubo ubuqotho bakho na? Mthuke uNkulunkulu uzifele!”<verse eid="JOB 2:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 2:10"/>Wamphendula wathi, “Ukhuluma njengomfazi oyisiwula. Sizakwamukela okuhle kuNkulunkulu singalwamukeli uhlupho na?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="JOB 2:10">Kukho konke lokhu uJobe kenzanga isono ngakutshoyo.<verse eid="JOB 2:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Abangane BakaJobe Abathathu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 2:11"/>Kwathi abangane bakaJobe abathathu, u-Elifazi umThemani, uBhilidadi umShuhi loZofari umNahama sebezwile ngazozonke inhlupho ezazimwele, basuka emakhaya abo bahlangana bavumelana ukuthi bahambe bayomqinisa njalo bamduduze. <verse eid="JOB 2:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 2:12"/>Bathi bembona besesebucwala kabaze bamazi; baqhinqa isililo, badabula izembatho zabo, bathela uthuli emakhanda abo. <verse eid="JOB 2:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 2:13"/>Basebehlala phansi laye okwensuku eziyisikhombisa lobusuku obuyisikhombisa. Kakho kubo owatsho ulutho kuye ngoba babona ubuhlungu obukhulu ayephakathi kwabo.<verse eid="JOB 2:13"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="JOB 3"/>
  <para style="s1">Inkulumo KaJobe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 3:1"/>Ngemva kwalokho uJobe wavula umlomo wakhe waliqalekisa ilanga azalwa ngalo. <verse eid="JOB 3:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 3:2"/>Wathi:<verse eid="JOB 3:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 3:3"/>“Sengathi ilanga lokuzalwa kwami lingatshabalala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:3">lalobobusuku okwathiwa, ‘Kuzelwe umfana!’<verse eid="JOB 3:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 3:4"/>Lolosuku sengathi lungaphenduka ubumnyama;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:4">sengathi uNkulunkulu ophezulu angangalunanzi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:4">lokukhanya kucime ngalo.<verse eid="JOB 3:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 3:5"/>Sengathi ubumnyama lethunzi elikhulu kungaluginya njalo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:5">sengathi iyezi lingalusibekela;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:5">sengathi umnyama ungalugubuzela.<verse eid="JOB 3:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 3:6"/>Lobobusuku, sengathi ubumnyama bungabuthi jwamu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:6">sengathi bungayekelwa ukubalwa kanye lezinsuku zomnyaka</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:6">futhi bungangeniswa lakuyiphi inyanga.<verse eid="JOB 3:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 3:7"/>Sengathi lobobusuku bungaba yinyumba;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:7">sengathi kungeze kwezwakala umsindo wentokozo ngalo.<verse eid="JOB 3:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 3:8"/>Sengathi labo abaqalekisa insuku bangaluqalekisa lolosuku,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:8">labo abazimisele ukuhlokoza uLeviyathani.<verse eid="JOB 3:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 3:9"/>Sengathi izinkanyezi zalo zokusa zingafiphala;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:9">lulindele imini kube yize</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:9">lungayiboni imisebe yokuqala yokusa,<verse eid="JOB 3:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 3:10"/>ngoba kaluyivalanga iminyango yesibeletho ngisiza</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:10">ukufihla uhlupho emehlweni ami.<verse eid="JOB 3:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 3:11"/>Kungani ngingafanga ngizalwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:11">ngahle ngacitsha ngisaphuma esiswini na?<verse eid="JOB 3:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 3:12"/>Kungani kwaba lamadolo okungemukela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:12">lamabele okungimunyisa na?<verse eid="JOB 3:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 3:13"/>Ngoba manje ngabe ngilele ekuthuleni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:13">ngabe ngisebuthongweni ekuphumuleni<verse eid="JOB 3:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 3:14"/>kanye lamakhosi lababusi bomhlaba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:14">ababezakhele izindawo okwamanje sezingamanxiwa,<verse eid="JOB 3:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 3:15"/>kanye lamakhosana ayelegolide,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:15">egcwalise izindlu zawo ngesiliva.<verse eid="JOB 3:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 3:16"/>Kumbe kungani ngingathukuzwanga emhlabathini njengomphunzo na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:16">njengosane oluvele lungazange lubone ukukhanya kosuku?<verse eid="JOB 3:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 3:17"/>Khonale ababi kabasaxokozeli,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:17">njalo khonale abakhatheleyo basekuphumuleni.<verse eid="JOB 3:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 3:18"/>Abathunjiweyo labo bazuza ukukhululeka;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:18">kabasakuzwa ukuhaladwa ngumtshayeli wabathunjiweyo.<verse eid="JOB 3:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 3:19"/>Abantukazana lezikhulu bakhonale,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:19">lesigqili siyakhululwa enkosini yaso.<verse eid="JOB 3:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 3:20"/>Kungani ukukhanya kuphiwa labo abasosizini na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:20">lokuphila kulabo abalobuhlungu emphefumulweni,<verse eid="JOB 3:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 3:21"/>kulabo abakhalela ukufa okungafikiyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:21">abakuthungathayo ukwedlula ingcebo efihliweyo,<verse eid="JOB 3:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 3:22"/>abaphuphuma ngenjabulo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:22">bathokoza nxa sebefika engcwabeni?<verse eid="JOB 3:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 3:23"/>Kungani impilo iphiwa umuntu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:23">ondlela yakhe ifihliwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:23">uNkulunkulu amhonqolozeleyo na?<verse eid="JOB 3:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 3:24"/>Ngoba ukububula sokuphenduke ukudla kwami kwansukuzonke;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:24">ukugomela kwami kuthululeka njengamanzi.<verse eid="JOB 3:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 3:25"/>Ebengikwesaba sekungehlele,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:25">obekungitshayisa ngovalo sekwenzakele kimi.<verse eid="JOB 3:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 3:26"/>Kangilakho ukuchelesa, kangilakho ukuthula;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:26">kangilakuphumula, kodwa ukuhlupheka kuphela.”<verse eid="JOB 3:26"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="JOB 4"/>
  <para style="s1">Impendulo Ka-Elifazi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 4:1"/>Wasephendula u-Elifazi umThemani wathi:<verse eid="JOB 4:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 4:2"/>“Nxa umuntu angaphosa ilizwi nje kuwe uzacunuka na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:2">Kodwa ngubani ongathula angakhulumi na?<verse eid="JOB 4:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 4:3"/>Khumbula ukuthi sewabafundisa njani abanengi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:3">ukuthi ubaqinise njani abalezandla ezibuthakathaka.<verse eid="JOB 4:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 4:4"/>Amazwi akho abasekele labo abakhubekayo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:4">uwaqinisile amadolo axegayo.<verse eid="JOB 4:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 4:5"/>Kodwa manje uhlupho luze kuwe, usuphela amandla;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:5">lukutshaya ubusudela ithemba.<verse eid="JOB 4:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 4:6"/>Kungani ukukholwa kwakho kungabi yiso isibindi sakho na</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:6">lezindlela zakho ezimsulwa zibe lithemba lakho na?<verse eid="JOB 4:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 4:7"/>Khumbula manje: Ngubani owathi engelacala wabhubha na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:7">Kungaphi lapho abaqotho abake babhujiswa khona na?<verse eid="JOB 4:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 4:8"/>Ngokubona kwami labo abalima okubi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:8">lalabo abahlanyela ububi bavuna bona.<verse eid="JOB 4:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 4:9"/>Ngokuphefumula kukaNkulunkulu bayabhubha;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:9">ngokukhwaza kolaka lwakhe bayafa.<verse eid="JOB 4:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 4:10"/>Izilwane zingabhonga zihwabhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:10">kodwa amazinyo ezilwane ezinkulu ayephuka.<verse eid="JOB 4:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 4:11"/>Isilwane siyafa ngokuswela ukudla</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:11">besekuthi imidlwane yesilwanekazi ihlakazeke.<verse eid="JOB 4:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 4:12"/>Kulethwe ilizwi kimi ngasese,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:12">indlebe zami zilizwile linyenyezwa.<verse eid="JOB 4:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 4:13"/>Phakathi kwamaphupho adungayo ebusuku,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:13">lapho abantu belele obukabhuka,<verse eid="JOB 4:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 4:14"/>ukwesaba lokuthuthumela kwangifikela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:14">kwenza wonke amathambo ami aqhaqhazela.<verse eid="JOB 4:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 4:15"/>Kwathi tshazi umoya emehlweni ami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:15">wahlasimula umzimba wami lenwele zami zema.<verse eid="JOB 4:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 4:16"/>Umoya lowo wema,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:16">kodwa kangikwazanga ukuthi kuyini.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 4:16">Kwakumi into phambi kwamehlo ami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:16">ngasengisizwa ilizwi elihelezayo:<verse eid="JOB 4:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 4:17"/>‘Kambe umuntu angalunga ukwedlula uNkulunkulu na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:17">Umuntu angahlanzeka kuloMenzi wakhe na?<verse eid="JOB 4:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 4:18"/>Nxa uNkulunkulu engazethembi izinceku zakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:18">nxa ebeka izingilosi zakhe umlandu ngokona,<verse eid="JOB 4:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 4:19"/>pho-ke kuzakuba njani kulabo abahlala ezindlini zodaka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:19">ozisekelo zazo zisothulini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:19">abahlifizeka lula njengenondo!<verse eid="JOB 4:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 4:20"/>Phakathi kokusa lokuhlwa bayabhidlizwa babe yizicucu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:20">bengananzwa langubani, bayabhubha kokuphela.<verse eid="JOB 4:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 4:21"/>Izintambo zamatende abo kazidonswa na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 4:21">bafe bengelalwazi?’ ”<verse eid="JOB 4:21"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="JOB 4"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" sid="JOB 5"/>
  <para style="s1">U-Elifazi Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 5:1"/>“Memeza nxa uthanda, kodwa ngubani ozakuphendula na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:1">Uzaphendukela kuwuphi wabangcwele na?<verse eid="JOB 5:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 5:2"/>Ukucaphuka kuyasibulala isiwula</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:2">lomhawu uyamqeda oyisithutha.<verse eid="JOB 5:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 5:3"/>Mina ngokwami sengasibona isiwula siphumelela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:3">kodwa masinyane nje indlu yaso yayisiqalekisiwe.<verse eid="JOB 5:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 5:4"/>Abantwabaso kabavikelekanga lakancinyane,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:4">baphoselwa entolongweni bengelamvikeli.<verse eid="JOB 5:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 5:5"/>Abalambileyo bayazidlela isivuno sakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:5">besithatha kanye lasemeveni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:5">labomileyo bahahabela inotho yakhe.<verse eid="JOB 5:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 5:6"/>Ngoba ubunzima kabugobhozi emhlabathini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:6">loba uhlupho luhlume phansi.<verse eid="JOB 5:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 5:7"/>Kodwa umuntu uzalelwa ukuhlupheka</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:7">njengoba ngeqiniso inhlansi zomlilo ziqhatshela phezulu.<verse eid="JOB 5:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 5:8"/>Kodwa aluba ubuyimi, bengizamncenga uNkulunkulu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:8">bengizakwethula udubo lwami kuye.<verse eid="JOB 5:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 5:9"/>Uyazenza izimanga ezingelakulinganiswa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:9">imimangaliso engelakubalwa.<verse eid="JOB 5:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 5:10"/>Uyanisa izulu emhlabeni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:10">uthumela amanzi elizweni.<verse eid="JOB 5:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 5:11"/>Abaphansi uyabakhweza phezulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:11">lalabo abakhalayo ubaphakamisela ekuphepheni.<verse eid="JOB 5:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 5:12"/>Uyawafubisa amacebo amaqili,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:12">ukuze izandla zawo zingaphumeleli.<verse eid="JOB 5:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 5:13"/>Uyababamba abahlakaniphileyo ebuqilini babo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:13">kuthi amaqhinga eziphoxo achitheke.<verse eid="JOB 5:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 5:14"/>Ubumnyama buyabehlela emini;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:14">phakathi kwemini bayaphumputha kungathi kusebusuku.<verse eid="JOB 5:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 5:15"/>Uyabasindisa abaswelayo baphephe inkemba emlonyeni wabo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:15">uyabasindisa ekubanjweni ngabalamandla.<verse eid="JOB 5:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 5:16"/>Ngakho abayanga balalo ithemba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:16">ukwahlulela kubi kuvala owakho umlomo.<verse eid="JOB 5:16"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 5:17"/>Ubusisiwe umuntu oqondiswa nguNkulunkulu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:17">ngakho ungaseyisi isijeziso sikaSomandla.<verse eid="JOB 5:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 5:18"/>Ngoba uyagwaza, kodwa aphinde abophe amanxeba;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:18">uyalimaza kodwa izandla zakhe njalo ziyapholisa.<verse eid="JOB 5:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 5:19"/>Uzakuhlenga ezinhluphekweni eziyisithupha;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:19">kweziyisikhombisa kawuyikuwelwa yingozi.<verse eid="JOB 5:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 5:20"/>Ngesikhathi sendlala uzakuhlenga ekufeni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:20">lasempini akuhlenge ekugaleleni kwenkemba.<verse eid="JOB 5:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 5:21"/>Uzavikelwa ekuhletshweni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:21">ungaze wesaba nxa kufika incithakalo.<verse eid="JOB 5:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 5:22"/>Uzakuhleka ukuchithakala kanye lendlala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:22">njalo ungaze wazesaba izilo zomhlaba.<verse eid="JOB 5:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 5:23"/>Ngoba uzakuba lesivumelwano lamatshe eganga,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:23">lezinyamazana zeganga zizahlalisana kuhle lawe.<verse eid="JOB 5:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 5:24"/>Uzakwazi ukuthi ithente lakho livikelekile;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:24">uzahlolisisa impahla yakho uthole kungelalutho olungekho.<verse eid="JOB 5:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 5:25"/>Uzakwazi ukuthi abantwabakho bazakuba banengi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:25">lesizukulwane sakho sibe ngangotshani bomhlaba.<verse eid="JOB 5:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 5:26"/>Uzakuza engcwabeni usukhulile okugcweleyo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:26">njengezikhwebu zamabele eziqoqwa seziphelele.<verse eid="JOB 5:26"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 5:27"/>Sesikuhlolile lokhu, kuliqiniso.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 5:27">Ngakho kuzwisise, ukulandele wena ngokwakho.”<verse eid="JOB 5:27"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 5"/>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" sid="JOB 6"/>
  <para style="s1">Impendulo KaJobe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 6:1"/>Wasephendula uJobe wathi:<verse eid="JOB 6:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 6:2"/>“Nxa ubuhlungu bami bungalinganiswa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:2">lokuhlupheka kwami konke kufakwe esikalini!<verse eid="JOB 6:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 6:3"/>Ngempela bungasinda ukwedlula itshebetshebe yolwandle,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:3">akungamangalisi ukuthi amazwi ami abhede kanje.<verse eid="JOB 6:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 6:4"/>Imitshoko kaSomandla iphakathi kwami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:4">umoya wami unatha itshefu yayo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:4">inhlupho zokuhlukuluza zikaNkulunkulu ziqondiswe kimi.<verse eid="JOB 6:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 6:5"/>Kambe ubabhemi weganga uyakhala yini utshani bukhona,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:5">loba inkabi ikhonye yona ukudla ilakho?<verse eid="JOB 6:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 6:6"/>Ukudla okuduma kuyadleka na kungelatswayi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:6">kumbe okumhlophe kweqanda kuyanambitheka yini?<verse eid="JOB 6:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 6:7"/>Ngiyala ukukuthinta;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:7">ukudla okunjalo kubuyisa inhliziyo yami.<verse eid="JOB 6:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 6:8"/>Oh, aluba ngingazuza isicelo sami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:8">uNkulunkulu angiphe lokho engikufisayo,<verse eid="JOB 6:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 6:9"/>ukuthi uNkulunkulu avume ukungichoboza,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:9">ekele nje isandla sakhe singiqede!<verse eid="JOB 6:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 6:10"/>Lalapho ngizabe ngilokhu ngilale induduzo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:10">intokozo yami ebuhlungwini obungadediyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:10">ukuthi bengingawaphikanga amazwi akhe oNgcwele.<verse eid="JOB 6:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 6:11"/>Ngilamandla bani okuthi ngibe lokhu ngithemba?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:11">Ngisamelelwe yini ukuba ngibe ngilokhu ngibekezela?<verse eid="JOB 6:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 6:12"/>Ngilamandla elitshe yini?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:12">Inyama yami ilithusi na?<verse eid="JOB 6:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 6:13"/>Ngilawo yini amandla okuzisiza,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:13">manje njengoba sengemukwe impumelelo?<verse eid="JOB 6:13"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 6:14"/>Iloba ngubani ogodla umusa kumkhula wakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:14">udela ukwesaba uSomandla.<verse eid="JOB 6:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 6:15"/>Kodwa abafowethu kabathenjwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:15">njengemifula egeleza icitsha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:15">njengemifula echithayo<verse eid="JOB 6:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 6:16"/>ileliqhwa eselincibilika,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:16">njalo igcwele ngongqwaqwane osencibilikile,<verse eid="JOB 6:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 6:17"/>kodwa ikhawule ukugeleza ngesikhathi sokoma,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:17">kuthi sekutshisa amanzi anyamalale ezindleleni zawo.<verse eid="JOB 6:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 6:18"/>Indwendwe zamakamela ziyaphambuka ezindleleni zazo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:18">zintule enkangala zifele khona.<verse eid="JOB 6:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 6:19"/>Indwendwe zamakamela aseThema zidinga amanzi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:19">abathengisi baseShebha balinde bethembile.<verse eid="JOB 6:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 6:20"/>Bayadana ngoba bebekade bethembile;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:20">bayafika khonale bafike badane.<verse eid="JOB 6:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 6:21"/>Lani selitshengise ukuthi kalilancedo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:21">libona into eyesabekayo beselisesaba.<verse eid="JOB 6:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 6:22"/>Sengake ngatsho yini ukuthi, ‘Ake lingihlawulele lokhu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:22">ngihlengani ngempahla yenu,<verse eid="JOB 6:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 6:23"/>ngikhululani esandleni sesitha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:23">ngihlengani ekufithizelweni ngabalesihluku’?<verse eid="JOB 6:23"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 6:24"/>Ngifundisani, ngizathula;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:24">ake lingitshengise lapho engiphambanise khona.<verse eid="JOB 6:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 6:25"/>Abuhlungu kanganani amazwi eqiniso!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:25">Kodwa ukuphikisa kwenu kutshengisani?<verse eid="JOB 6:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 6:26"/>Lizama ukuqondisa engikutshoyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:26">amazwi omuntu oselahlekelwe lithemba liwathethe njengomoya nje na?<verse eid="JOB 6:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 6:27"/>Lina lingenza inkatho ngezintandane,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:27">lithengise lomngane wenu.<verse eid="JOB 6:27"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 6:28"/>Kodwa okwamanje wobani lomusa lingizwele.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:28">Ngingaqamba amanga phambi kwenu na?<verse eid="JOB 6:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOB 6:29"/>Dedani, lingenzi okungaqondanga;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:29">khumbulani kutsha, phela ubuqotho bami busengozini.<verse eid="JOB 6:29"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOB 6:30"/>Kukhona okubi na okusezindebeni zami?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 6:30">Kambe umlomo wami kawukwehlukanisi okubi na?”<verse eid="JOB 6:30"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="JOB 6"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" sid="JOB 7"/>
  <para style="s1">UJobe Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 7:1"/>“Umuntu kakho ekutshikatshikeni okunzima yini emhlabeni?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:1">Insuku zakhe kazifani lezomuntu oqhatshiweyo na?<verse eid="JOB 7:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 7:2"/>Njengesigqili siloyisa amathunzi okuhlwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:2">lanjengoqhatshiweyo elindele umholo wakhe,<verse eid="JOB 7:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 7:3"/>kanjalo ngibekelwe izinyanga ezingelambadalo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:3">lobusuku bosizi sebabelwe mina.<verse eid="JOB 7:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 7:4"/>Ngithi nxa ngilala ngicabange ngithi, ‘Kuzakusa nini na’?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:4">Ubusuku buyadonsa ngiqwayize kuze kuse.<verse eid="JOB 7:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 7:5"/>Umzimba wami uphihlika impethu lamathuthuva,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:5">isikhumba sami siyobukile siyabhibhidla.<verse eid="JOB 7:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 7:6"/>Insuku zami ziyaphangisa kulosungulo lomaluki,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:6">zisuka ziphele kungekho ithemba.<verse eid="JOB 7:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 7:7"/>Khumbula, Oh Nkulunkulu, ukuthi impilo yami ngumoya nje;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:7">amehlo ami kawayikufa akubona njalo ukuthokoza.<verse eid="JOB 7:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 7:8"/>Ilihlo elingibonayo khathesi alisayikuphinde lingibone futhi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:8">lizangidinga, kodwa ngizakuba ngingasekho.<verse eid="JOB 7:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 7:9"/>Njengeyezi elinyamalalayo liphele,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:9">kanjalo lowo ongena engcwabeni kaphenduki.<verse eid="JOB 7:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 7:10"/>Kasoze lanini aphinde angene endlini yakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:10">indawo yakhe kayisayikubuye imazi lanini.<verse eid="JOB 7:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 7:11"/>Ngakho-ke kangizukuthula;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:11">ngizakhuluma ubuhlungu obusemoyeni wami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:11">ngizasola ngokudabuka komphefumulo wami.<verse eid="JOB 7:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 7:12"/>Ngilulwandle yini, kumbe ngiyisilo semanzini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:12">okungaze lihlale lingilindile?<verse eid="JOB 7:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 7:13"/>Ngithi lapho ngicabanga ukuthi umbheda wami uzangiduduza</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:13">lecansi lami liphungule ukusola kwami,<verse eid="JOB 7:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 7:14"/>lakhona lapho liyangethusa ngamaphupho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:14">njalo lingethusele ngemibono,<verse eid="JOB 7:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 7:15"/>okwenza ngiqome ukuklinywa lokufa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:15">kulalo umzimba wami.<verse eid="JOB 7:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 7:16"/>Ngiyayeyisa impilo yami; kangiloyisi ukuphila okwaphakade.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:16">Ngiyekelani; insuku zami kazisatsho lutho.<verse eid="JOB 7:16"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 7:17"/>Umuntu uyini ongaze uzihluphe kangaka ngaye,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:17">ungaze umnake kangaka,<verse eid="JOB 7:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 7:18"/>uze umhlole ekuseni insuku zonke</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:18">njalo umlinge imizuzwana yonke na?<verse eid="JOB 7:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 7:19"/>Kawusoze uke ukhangele eceleni kwami na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:19">loba uke ungixekele okomzuzwana yini?<verse eid="JOB 7:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 7:20"/>Aluba ngenze isono, kuyini engikwenzileyo kuwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:20">wena mlindi wabantu?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 7:20">Kungani ukhethe ukuhlukuluza mina na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:20">Sengingumthwalo kuwe na?<verse eid="JOB 7:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 7:21"/>Kungani ungaxoleli iziphambeko zami na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:21">uthethelele izono zami?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 7:21">Ngoba kakusekhatshana ukuthi ngilale othulini;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 7:21">uzangidinga, kanti ngizabe ngingasekho.”<verse eid="JOB 7:21"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 7"/>
  <chapter number="8" style="c" sid="JOB 8"/>
  <para style="s1">Inkulumo KaBhilidadi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 8:1"/>UBhilidadi umShuhi wasephendula wathi:<verse eid="JOB 8:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 8:2"/>“Koze kube nini ukhuluma izinto ezinjalo?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:2">Amazwi akho angumoya ophenquzayo.<verse eid="JOB 8:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 8:3"/>Kambe uNkulunkulu uyakuhlanekela ukulunga na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:3">Kambe uSomandla uyakuhlanekela okuhle na?<verse eid="JOB 8:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 8:4"/>Lapho abantwabakho besona kuye,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:4">wabapha isijeziso sokona kwabo.<verse eid="JOB 8:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 8:5"/>Kanti nxa wena uzakhangela kuNkulunkulu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:5">uncenge kuSomandla,<verse eid="JOB 8:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 8:6"/>nxa umsulwa ulungile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:6">lamanje nje uzaphakama akusize</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:6">akubuyisele esimeni sakho.<verse eid="JOB 8:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 8:7"/>Lapho owaqalisa khona kuzakhanya sekukuncinyane,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:7">ngoba ngezinsuku ezizayo uzabe usuphumelela kakhulu.<verse eid="JOB 8:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 8:8"/>Buza izizukulwane ezingaphambili</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:8">udinge ukuthi okhokho babo bafundani,<verse eid="JOB 8:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 8:9"/>ngoba thina sizelwe izolo nje, kasazi lutho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:9">lezinsuku zethu emhlabeni zilithunzi kuphela.<verse eid="JOB 8:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 8:10"/>Kambe kaziyikukulaya zikutshele na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:10">Kaziyikuletha amazwi okuzwisisa na?<verse eid="JOB 8:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 8:11"/>Konje imihlanga ingakhula ibe mide ingekho exhaphozini na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:11">Imizi ingaphila kungelamanzi na?<verse eid="JOB 8:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 8:12"/>Nxa leyonqodi isakhula ingakaqunywa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:12">imane ibune masinyane kulotshani.<verse eid="JOB 8:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 8:13"/>Sinjalo isiphetho sabo bonke abakhohlwa uNkulunkulu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:13">litshabalala kanjalo ithemba lalowo ongakholwayo.<verse eid="JOB 8:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 8:14"/>Lokho akuthembayo kufohlozeka lula;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:14">lokho eyeme kukho yibulembu besayobe.<verse eid="JOB 8:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 8:15"/>Uyeyama kulobubulembu bakhe, kodwa bubhidlike;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:15">uyabambelela kubo, kodwa bukhithike.<verse eid="JOB 8:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 8:16"/>Unjengesihlahla esithelelwa kakhulu sikhula elangeni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:16">esisabalalisa ingatsha zaso esivandeni;<verse eid="JOB 8:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 8:17"/>sinxibanise impande zaso enqunjini yamatshe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:17">sizama ukuzuza ukugxila kuhle ematsheni.<verse eid="JOB 8:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 8:18"/>Kodwa singasitshulwa kuleyondawo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:18">leyondawo isisilandula ithi, ‘Angikaze ngikubone.’<verse eid="JOB 8:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 8:19"/>Ngeqiniso impilo yaso iyabuna,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:19">ezinye izihlahla zibe zilokhu zikhula emhlabathini lowo.<verse eid="JOB 8:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 8:20"/>Ngeqiniso uNkulunkulu kamlahli umuntu ongelasici</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:20">futhi kaqinisi izandla zezigangi.<verse eid="JOB 8:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 8:21"/>Usazogcwalisa umlomo wakho ngohleko</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:21">lezindebe zakho ngokumemeza ngentokozo.<verse eid="JOB 8:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 8:22"/>Izitha zakho zizakwembathiswa ngehlazo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 8:22">lamathente ababi azatshabalala.”<verse eid="JOB 8:22"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 8"/>
  <chapter number="9" style="c" sid="JOB 9"/>
  <para style="s1">Impendulo KaJobe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 9:1"/>Wasephendula uJobe wathi:<verse eid="JOB 9:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 9:2"/>“Ngeqiniso ngiyazi ukuthi lokhu kuliqiniso.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:2">Kodwa umuntu wenyama angalunga yini kuNkulunkulu?<verse eid="JOB 9:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 9:3"/>Loba umuntu ubengafisa ukuphikisana laye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:3">ngeke amphendule lakanye emibuzweni eyinkulungwane.<verse eid="JOB 9:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 9:4"/>Ukuhlakanipha kwakhe kujulile, amandla akhe makhulu.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:4">Ngubani kambe oke wamelana laye wasinda?<verse eid="JOB 9:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 9:5"/>Uyazidudula izintaba zona zingazi lutho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:5">azigenqule nxa esezondile.<verse eid="JOB 9:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 9:6"/>Uyawunyikinya umhlaba endaweni yawo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:6">axukuxe izinsika zawo.<verse eid="JOB 9:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 9:7"/>Uyalitshela ilanga ukuba lingakhanyi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:7">asibekele ukukhanya kwezinkanyezi.<verse eid="JOB 9:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 9:8"/>Nguye kuphela owelula amazulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:8">ohamba phezu kwamagagasi olwandle.<verse eid="JOB 9:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 9:9"/>UnguMenzi wezinkanyezi iNgulube leZinja,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:9">iSilimela lomthala waseningizimu.<verse eid="JOB 9:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 9:10"/>Wenza imimangaliso engafinyelelekiyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:10">izimanga ezingelakubalwa.<verse eid="JOB 9:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 9:11"/>Uthi nxa esedlula kimi, ngingamboni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:11">ahambe khonapho ngingezwa lutho.<verse eid="JOB 9:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 9:12"/>Nxa ehluthuna, ngubani ongamalela?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:12">Ngubani ongathi kuye, ‘Wenzani wena?’<verse eid="JOB 9:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 9:13"/>UNkulunkulu kalunqandi ulaka lwakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:13">labasekeli bakaRahabi besaba bawela ezinyaweni zakhe.<verse eid="JOB 9:13"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 9:14"/>Pho mina ngingaphikisana laye njani?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:14">Ngingawathatha ngaphi amazwi okujijana laye?<verse eid="JOB 9:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 9:15"/>Laloba ngingelamlandu, ngeke ngimphendule;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:15">ngingancenga uMahluleli wami kuphela ukuthi angihawukele.<verse eid="JOB 9:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 9:16"/>Lanxa bengingambiza asabele,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:16">angikholwa ukuthi ubengangilalela.<verse eid="JOB 9:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 9:17"/>Ubengangicobodisa ngesiphepho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:17">andise amanxeba ami kungelasizatho.<verse eid="JOB 9:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 9:18"/>Ubengasoze angiphe ithuba lokukhokha umoya</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:18">kodwa ubezahle angincindezele ngosizi.<verse eid="JOB 9:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 9:19"/>Nxa kungokwamandla, alamandla amakhulu!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:19">Nxa kungokokwahlulela ngokulunga, ngubani ongamthonisisa?<verse eid="JOB 9:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 9:20"/>Loba ngingabe ngimsulwa, umlomo wami ubungangilahla;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:20">lanxa ngimsulwa wona ubuzakuthi ngilecala.<verse eid="JOB 9:20"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 9:21"/>Lanxa ngingelacala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:21">angizihluphi ngami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:21">ngiyayeyisa impilo yami.<verse eid="JOB 9:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 9:22"/>Kuyafanana konke; yikho ngisithi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:22">‘Ubhubhisa bonke abangelacala lababi.’<verse eid="JOB 9:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 9:23"/>Nxa isifo esibi sibulala ngokuphangisa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:23">uyabahleka abangelacala ngokulahla kwabo ithemba.<verse eid="JOB 9:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 9:24"/>Nxa ilizwe liwela ezandleni zababi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:24">wembesa amehlo abahluleli balo.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:24">Nxa kungayisuye, pho ngubani?<verse eid="JOB 9:24"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 9:25"/>Amalanga ami alesiqubu esidlula esesithunywa;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:25">ayaphapha anyamalale kungela mthonselanyana wokuthokoza.<verse eid="JOB 9:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 9:26"/>Antweza edlule njengezikepe zelala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:26">njengenkozi zisehla zihwitha ezikudlayo.<verse eid="JOB 9:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 9:27"/>Nxa ngingathi, ‘Ngizakubeka eceleni ukusola kwami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:27">ngicitshe ukunyukubala kwami, ngibobotheke,’<verse eid="JOB 9:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 9:28"/>ngilokhu ngihemahema ngezinhlupho zami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:28">ngoba ngiyazi ukuthi kawuzukungigeza.<verse eid="JOB 9:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOB 9:29"/>Njengoba ngivele sengibekwe icala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:29">ngizazihluphelani ngokulwela ize na?<verse eid="JOB 9:29"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOB 9:30"/>Loba ngingaze ngigeze ngesepa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:30">lezandla zami ngesoda yokuhlambulula,<verse eid="JOB 9:30"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOB 9:31"/>uzavele ungiphosele emgodini olodaka</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:31">ngize ngenyanywe yizigqoko zami.<verse eid="JOB 9:31"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOB 9:32"/>Akasumuntu njengami ukuthi ngingamphendula,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:32">ukuthi singamisana emthethwandaba.<verse eid="JOB 9:32"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOB 9:33"/>Aluba ubengabakhona osilamulayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:33">abeke isandla sakhe phezu kwethu sobabili,<verse eid="JOB 9:33"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="JOB 9:34"/>omunye nje ongasusa uswazi lukaNkulunkulu kimi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:34">ukuze ngingatshukunyiswa yikwesaba lokhu.<verse eid="JOB 9:34"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="JOB 9:35"/>Lapho-ke bengizakhuluma ngingesabi yena,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 9:35">kodwa okwakhathesi kunje, ngeke.”<verse eid="JOB 9:35"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="JOB 9"/>
  <chapter number="10" style="c" sid="JOB 10"/>
  <para style="s1">UJobe Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 10:1"/>“Senginengwa yimpilo yami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:1">ngakho sengizasola ngingasathikazi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:1">ngithulule ubuhlungu bomphefumulo wami.<verse eid="JOB 10:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 10:2"/>Ngizakuthi kuNkulunkulu: Ungangilahli,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:2">kodwa ngitshela ukuthi ungethesa cala bani.<verse eid="JOB 10:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 10:3"/>Kuyakuthabisa na ukungizwisa ubuhlungu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:3">ukulahla umsebenzi wezandla zakho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:3">ikanti uyahlekelela ngamacebo ababi?<verse eid="JOB 10:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 10:4"/>Ulamehlo enyama na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:4">Ubona njengokubona kwabantu na?<verse eid="JOB 10:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 10:5"/>Insuku zakho ziyafanana lezabantu yini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:5">kumbe iminyaka yakho njengeyomuntu yini,<verse eid="JOB 10:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 10:6"/>osungaze uphenye iziphambeko zami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:6">njalo ulandelele isono sami,<verse eid="JOB 10:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 10:7"/>loba wena ukwazi ukuthi angilacala</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:7">lokuthi kakho ongangikhulula esandleni sakho?<verse eid="JOB 10:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 10:8"/>Izandla zakho zangibumba zangenza.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:8">Pho usuzaphenduka ungibhidlize na?<verse eid="JOB 10:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 10:9"/>Khumbula ukuthi wangibumba njengomdaka.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:9">Pho usuzabuye ungiphendule uthuli na?<verse eid="JOB 10:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 10:10"/>Kawungichithanga yini njengochago</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:10">njalo wangijiyisa njengolaza,<verse eid="JOB 10:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 10:11"/>wangigqokisa ngesikhumba lenyama,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:11">wangithungela ndawonye ngamathambo lemisipha?<verse eid="JOB 10:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 10:12"/>Wangipha ukuphila wangitshengisa umusa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:12">ukunanza kwakho kwawelusa umoya wami.<verse eid="JOB 10:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 10:13"/>Kodwa lokhu yikho owakufihla enhliziyweni yakho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:13">njalo ngiyazi ukuthi lokhu kwakukhona engqondweni yakho:<verse eid="JOB 10:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 10:14"/>Nxa ngona, ngabe wawungikhangele</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:14">wawungeke wekela ukona kwami kungajeziswa.<verse eid="JOB 10:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 10:15"/>Aluba ngilecala, maye mina!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:15">Laloba ngimsulwa, akukho engingakwenza,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 10:15">ngoba ngiyafa ngenhloni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:15">njalo ngiyagalula ekuhluphekeni kwami.<verse eid="JOB 10:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 10:16"/>Nxa ngingathi ngivusa ikhanda ungicwathela njengesilwane</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:16">uphinde utshengise amandla akho esabekayo kimi.<verse eid="JOB 10:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 10:17"/>Uletha ofakazi abatsha abangilahlayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:17">wandise ulaka lwakho kimi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:17">amabutho akho angihlasela amaviyo ngamaviyo.<verse eid="JOB 10:17"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 10:18"/>Pho kungani wangikhupha esibelethweni na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:18">Ngifisa ukuthi ngabe ngafa ngingakabonwa laloba yiliphi ilihlo.<verse eid="JOB 10:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 10:19"/>Aluba ngavele ngingabi ngophilayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:19">loba ngathwalwa ngisuka esibelethweni ngasiwa ethuneni!<verse eid="JOB 10:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 10:20"/>Insuku zami ezilutshwane kaseziphelile nje?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:20">Akungifulathele ukuze ngizuze umzuzwana wentokozo nje<verse eid="JOB 10:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 10:21"/>ngingakayi lapho okungabuywa khona,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:21">elizweni lobumnyama lethunzi elikhulu,<verse eid="JOB 10:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 10:22"/>elizweni lobusuku obujule ngempela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:22">elethunzi elinzima lengxubevange,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 10:22">lapho lokukhanya kunjengobumnyama.”<verse eid="JOB 10:22"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 10"/>
  <chapter number="11" style="c" sid="JOB 11"/>
  <para style="s1">Impendulo KaZofari</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 11:1"/>UZofari umNahama wasephendula wathi:<verse eid="JOB 11:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 11:2"/>“Uthi amazwi wonke la angayekelwa ukuphendulwa na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:2">Uwawane lolu luyekelwe nje lubheda?<verse eid="JOB 11:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 11:3"/>Umbhedo wakho lo ungenza abantu bathule na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:3">Uthi ungangakhuzwa muntu wena ukhulumela eceleni?<verse eid="JOB 11:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 11:4"/>Uthi kuNkulunkulu, ‘Inkolo yami kayilansolo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:4">njalo ngimsulwa phambi kwakho.’<verse eid="JOB 11:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 11:5"/>Oh, ngize ngifise ukuthi ngabe uNkulunkulu uyakhuluma,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:5">avule izindebe zakhe ekusola<verse eid="JOB 11:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 11:6"/>akuvulele imfihlo zokuhlakanipha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:6">ngoba inhlakanipho yeqiniso ikabili.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 11:6">Yazi lokhu:</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:6">UNkulunkulu uvele usezikhohliwe ezinye izono zakho.<verse eid="JOB 11:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 11:7"/>Kambe ungayifinyelela yini imfihlakalo kaNkulunkulu?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:7">Ungaziphenya iziphetho zikaSomandla na?<verse eid="JOB 11:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 11:8"/>Ziqongile ngaphezu kwamazulu, ungenzani kambe?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:8">Zizikile kulokujula kolwandle, kuyini ongakwazi pho?<verse eid="JOB 11:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 11:9"/>Ukulinganiswa kwazo kude kulomhlaba</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:9">njalo kubanzi kulolwandle.<verse eid="JOB 11:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 11:10"/>Nxa engeza lapha akuphosele entolongweni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:10">abize inkundla, ngubani ongamphikisa na?<verse eid="JOB 11:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 11:11"/>Liqiniso ukuthi uyababona abantu abakhohlisayo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:11">njalo nxa ebona okubi, kananzeleli na?<verse eid="JOB 11:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 11:12"/>Kodwa umuntu oyisithutha ngeke ahlakaniphe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:12">njengoba ubabhemi weganga engeke azalwa ngumuntu.<verse eid="JOB 11:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 11:13"/>Kodwa nxa ugxilisa inhliziyo yakho kuye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:13">uphakamisele izandla zakho kuye,<verse eid="JOB 11:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 11:14"/>nxa ulahla isono esisesandleni sakho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:14">ungavumeli bubi buhlale ethenteni lakho,<verse eid="JOB 11:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 11:15"/>lapho-ke uzabuveza ubuso bakho ungelanhloni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:15">uzakuma uqine ungesabi.<verse eid="JOB 11:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 11:16"/>Uzalukhohlwa ngempela uhlupho lwakho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:16">lufike nje engqondweni njengezikhukhula ezadlulayo.<verse eid="JOB 11:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 11:17"/>Impilo izakhanya kulemini enkulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:17">lobumnyama buzakuba njengasekuseni.<verse eid="JOB 11:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 11:18"/>Uzavikeleka, ngoba ithemba likhona;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:18">uzakhangela ofuna khona uzuze ukuphumula uvikelekile.<verse eid="JOB 11:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 11:19"/>Uzazilalela, kungekho okwethusayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:19">njalo abanengi bazabe sebezisondeza kuwe.<verse eid="JOB 11:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 11:20"/>Kodwa amehlo ababi azafiphala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:20">behluleke lokubaleka;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:20">ithemba labo libe yikuhotsha umoya wokufa.”<verse eid="JOB 11:20"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 11"/>
  <chapter number="12" style="c" sid="JOB 12"/>
  <para style="s1">Impendulo KaJobe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 12:1"/>Wasephendula uJobe wathi:<verse eid="JOB 12:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 12:2"/>“Wo, lina yini elizibona kuyini abantu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:2">njalo lolwazi luzakufa lani!<verse eid="JOB 12:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 12:3"/>Kodwa lami ngilayo ingqondo njengani;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:3">kalingedluli ngalutho.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:3">Ngubani ongazaziyo izinto zonke lezi?<verse eid="JOB 12:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 12:4"/>Sengiyinto yokuhlekisa ebanganini bami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:4">lanxa ngacela kuNkulunkulu waphendula,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:4">inhlekisa sibili, kodwa ngilungile, ngimsulwa!<verse eid="JOB 12:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 12:5"/>Abantu abahlezi kuhle bayakweyisa ukwehlelwa ngumnyama,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:5">bathi kuyimfanelo yalabo onyawo zabo sezitshelela.<verse eid="JOB 12:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 12:6"/>Amathente ezigebenga avikelekile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:6">lalabo abamthukuthelisayo uNkulunkulu bavikelekile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:6">uNkulunkulu ulabo ezandleni zakhe.<verse eid="JOB 12:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 12:7"/>Kodwa ake ubuze izinyamazana, zizakufundisa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:7">kumbe izinyoni zemoyeni, zizakutshela;<verse eid="JOB 12:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 12:8"/>kumbe khuluma lomhlaba, uzakufundisa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:8">loba uthi inhlanzi zolwandle zikwazise.<verse eid="JOB 12:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 12:9"/>Yikuphi kwalezizinto okungaziyo na</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:9">ukuthi yisandla <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> esikwenzileyo lokhu?<verse eid="JOB 12:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 12:10"/>Esandleni sakhe kulempilo yazo zonke izidalwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:10">lokuphefumula kwabantu bonke.<verse eid="JOB 12:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 12:11"/>Indlebe kayiwahloli yini wonke amazwi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:11">njengolimi lunambitha ukudla?<verse eid="JOB 12:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 12:12"/>Angithi ukuhlakanipha kufunyanwa ebadaleni na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:12">Angithi impilo ende iletha ukuzwisisa na?<verse eid="JOB 12:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 12:13"/>NgokukaNkulunkulu ukuhlakanipha lamandla;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:13">ukweluleka lokuzwisisa kungokwakhe.<verse eid="JOB 12:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 12:14"/>Lokho akubhidlizayo kungeke kwamiswa njalo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:14">lowo amvalelayo ngeke avulelwe.<verse eid="JOB 12:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 12:15"/>Angaze awavale amanzi, kuba lokoma;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:15">angawavulela kuba lomonakalo elizweni.<verse eid="JOB 12:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 12:16"/>Angawakhe amandla lenhlakanipho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:16">okhohliswayo lomkhohlisi ngabakhe bonke.<verse eid="JOB 12:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 12:17"/>Abeluleki uyabakhupha bahambe beze</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:17">enze abehluleli babe yiziphukuphuku.<verse eid="JOB 12:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 12:18"/>Uyanyomula izibopho ezibotshwe ngamakhosi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:18">azibophe ngelembu ekhalweni.<verse eid="JOB 12:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 12:19"/>Abaphristi uyabakhupha beze</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:19">awagenqule amadoda abesithi asegxilile.<verse eid="JOB 12:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 12:20"/>Uyazithulisa izindebe zabeluleki</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:20">abathenjiweyo asuse ulwazi lwabadala.<verse eid="JOB 12:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 12:21"/>Izikhulu uzihleka usulu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:21">abalamandla abathathele lawomandla.<verse eid="JOB 12:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 12:22"/>Uyembula imfihlo ezenzeka emnyameni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:22">amathunzi azikileyo awalethe ekukhanyeni.<verse eid="JOB 12:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 12:23"/>Wenza izizwe zikhule, abesezidiliza;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:23">uyaziqhelisa izizwe, aphinde azichithe.<verse eid="JOB 12:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 12:24"/>Abakhokheli basemhlabeni ubemuka ukuhlakanipha kwabo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:24">ubenza bantule enkangala.<verse eid="JOB 12:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 12:25"/>Bayaphumputha emnyameni kungelakukhanya;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:25">ubenza badiyazele njengezidakwa.”<verse eid="JOB 12:25"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="JOB 12"/>
  <chapter number="13" style="c" sid="JOB 13"/>
  <para style="s1">UJobe Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 13:1"/>“Amehlo ami asekubonile konke lokhu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:1">indlebe zami zikuzwile zakuqedisisa lokhu.<verse eid="JOB 13:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 13:2"/>Elikwaziyo lina lami ngiyakwazi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:2">kalingcono ngalutho kulami.<verse eid="JOB 13:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 13:3"/>Kodwa ngiloyisa ukukhuluma loSomandla,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:3">ngiphikisane loNkulunkulu ngendaba yami.<verse eid="JOB 13:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 13:4"/>Kodwa lina lingigcona ngamanga;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:4">lonke lizinyanga ezingelamsebenzi!<verse eid="JOB 13:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 13:5"/>Thulani lithi zwi lonke!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:5">Lokho kungaba yikuhlakanipha kini.<verse eid="JOB 13:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 13:6"/>Zwanini-ke manje engikutshoyo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:6">lalelani ukuncenga kwezindebe zami.<verse eid="JOB 13:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 13:7"/>Lingakhuluma okubi limele uNkulunkulu na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:7">Lingamkhulumela inkohliso na?<verse eid="JOB 13:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 13:8"/>Limtshengisa ukuthi liyabandlulula yini?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:8">Yini elimkhulumelayo uNkulunkulu akutshoyo?<verse eid="JOB 13:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 13:9"/>Kungalilungela yini nxa engalihlola?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:9">Kambe lingamkhohlisa njengoba lingakhohlisa abantu na?<verse eid="JOB 13:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 13:10"/>Ngempela angaligcona</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:10">nxa lingabe litshengisa ukubandlulula.<verse eid="JOB 13:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 13:11"/>Inkazimulo yakhe ingezake ilethuse na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:11">Ukwesabeka kwakhe kungezake kulehlele na?<verse eid="JOB 13:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 13:12"/>Izitsho zenu ziyizaga zomlotha;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:12">lezivikelo zenu yizivikelo zebumba kuphela.<verse eid="JOB 13:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 13:13"/>Thulani ngikhulume mina;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:13">kungivelele loba kuyini okuvelayo.<verse eid="JOB 13:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 13:14"/>Ngizifakelani engozini na</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:14">ngiphathe impilo yami ezandleni zami?<verse eid="JOB 13:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 13:15"/>Lanxa engangibulala kodwa ngizakwala ngimethemba;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:15">ngizazivikela izindlela zami phambi kwakhe.<verse eid="JOB 13:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 13:16"/>Ngeqiniso lokhu kuzangihlenga,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:16">ngoba kakho umuntu ongakholwayo ongasondela kuye!<verse eid="JOB 13:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 13:17"/>Ake lilalele kuhle amazwi ami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:17">vulani indlebe zenu lizwe engikutshoyo.<verse eid="JOB 13:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 13:18"/>Manje-ke njengoba sengiyilungisile indaba yami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:18">ngiyabona ukuthi ngizakhululwa.<verse eid="JOB 13:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 13:19"/>Ngubani kambe ongangethesa icala?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:19">Nxa ekhona, ngizathula ngife.<verse eid="JOB 13:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 13:20"/>Akungiphe lezizinto ezimbili nje, Oh Nkulunkulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:20">lapho-ke angiyikukucatshela:<verse eid="JOB 13:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 13:21"/>Sisusele khatshana lami isandla sakho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:21">ukhawule ukungethusa ngokwesabeka kwakho.<verse eid="JOB 13:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 13:22"/>Ubusungibizela ecaleni, ngizaphendula,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:22">kumbe ungiyekele ngikhulume, lawe uphendule.<verse eid="JOB 13:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 13:23"/>Sengenze iziphambeko lezono ezinganani na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:23">Ngitshengisa isiphambeko sami lesono sami.<verse eid="JOB 13:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 13:24"/>Kungani ufihla ubuso bakho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:24">ungithathe njengesitha sakho?<verse eid="JOB 13:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 13:25"/>Uzahluphana lehlamvu eliphetshulwa ngumoya na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:25">Uzaxotshana lomule owomileyo na?<verse eid="JOB 13:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 13:26"/>Ngoba ubhala izinto ezibuhlungu ngami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:26">ungenze ngivune izono zobutsha bami.<verse eid="JOB 13:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 13:27"/>Ukhina inyawo zami ngezibopho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:27">ulandelela zonke izindlela zami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:27">ngokudweba uphawu ezinyathelweni zezinyawo zami.<verse eid="JOB 13:27"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 13:28"/>Yikho-ke umuntu ecikizeka njengento ebolileyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:28">njengesigqoko esidliwe yinondo.”<verse eid="JOB 13:28"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="JOB 13"/>
  <chapter number="14" style="c" sid="JOB 14"/>
  <para style="s1">UJobe Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 14:1"/>“Umuntu ozelwe ngumfazi ulensuku ezilutshwane</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:1">njalo ezigcwele inhlupho.<verse eid="JOB 14:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 14:2"/>Uyaqhakaza njengeluba aphinde abune;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:2">njengesithunzi esithi tshazi, akemi.<verse eid="JOB 14:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 14:3"/>Onjalo ungala ulokhu umkhangele na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:3">Ungamisa phambi kwakho umthonisise na?<verse eid="JOB 14:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 14:4"/>Ngubani ongaveza okuhlambulukileyo kokungcolileyo na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:4">Kakho!<verse eid="JOB 14:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 14:5"/>Insuku zomuntu zimisiwe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:5">uzibekile izinyanga zokuphila kwakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:5">wabeka lemikhawulo angeke ayeqe.<verse eid="JOB 14:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 14:6"/>Ngakho-ke myekele ungazihluphi ngaye,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:6">aze aqede lesosikhathi sakhe njengomuntu oqhatshiweyo.<verse eid="JOB 14:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 14:7"/>Kungaba lethemba ngesihlahla;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:7">singaganyulwa siyahluma njalo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:7">amahlumela aso kawayikwehluleka ukukhula.<verse eid="JOB 14:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 14:8"/>Impande zaso zingaguga phansi emhlabathini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:8">lesiphunzi saso sife emhlabathini,<verse eid="JOB 14:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 14:9"/>kodwa singezwa amanzi siyahluma</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:9">sikhuphe ingatsha njengesihlahla esitsha.<verse eid="JOB 14:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 14:10"/>Kodwa umuntu uyafa alaliswe phansi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:10">uphefumula okokucina angabe esabakhona.<verse eid="JOB 14:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 14:11"/>Njengamanzi esitsha olwandle</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:11">lanjengomfula ucitsha amanzi wome qha,<verse eid="JOB 14:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 14:12"/>ngokunjalo umuntu ulala phansi angabe esavuka;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:12">kuze kutshabalale amazulu abantu kabayikuvuka</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:12">kumbe baphatshanyiswe ebuthongweni babo.<verse eid="JOB 14:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 14:13"/>Kube uyangifihla ethuneni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:13">ungithukuze ulaka lwakho luze ludlule!</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 14:13">Kube ungibekela isikhathi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:13">ube usungikhumbula!<verse eid="JOB 14:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 14:14"/>Umuntu angafa uphinde aphile na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:14">Zonke insuku zokutshikatshika kwami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:14">ngizalindela isikhathi sokuyekelwa kwami.<verse eid="JOB 14:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 14:15"/>Uzabiza lami ngizasabela;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:15">uzasifisa lesosidalwa esenziwa yizandla zakho.<verse eid="JOB 14:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 14:16"/>Ngeqiniso lapho uzabala izinyathelo zami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:16">kodwa kawuyikulandelela izono zami.<verse eid="JOB 14:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 14:17"/>Iziphambeko zami zizananyekwa emgodleni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:17">uzasigubuzela isono sami.<verse eid="JOB 14:17"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 14:18"/>Kodwa njengentaba ikhumuzeka ize ibhidlike,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:18">lanjengedwala ligudluka endaweni yalo,<verse eid="JOB 14:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 14:19"/>njengamanzi awagubhayo amatshe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:19">lezikhukhula zikhukhula umhlabathi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:19">kanjalo uyalibhidliza ithemba lomuntu.<verse eid="JOB 14:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 14:20"/>Umehlula kanye angaphindi abekhona, adlule;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:20">uyabuguqula ubuso bakho umxotshe.<verse eid="JOB 14:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 14:21"/>Nxa amadodana akhe ezuza udumo, kawakwazi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:21">nxa izizukulwane zakhe zisehliswa, kazikuboni.<verse eid="JOB 14:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 14:22"/>Bezwa kuphela ubuhlungu bemizimba yabo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 14:22">bazikhalele bona.”<verse eid="JOB 14:22"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 14"/>
  <chapter number="15" style="c" sid="JOB 15"/>
  <para style="s1">Impendulo Ka-Elifazi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 15:1"/>Wasephendula u-Elifazi umThemani wathi:<verse eid="JOB 15:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 15:2"/>“Kambe indoda ehlakaniphileyo ingaphendula ngeze nje</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:2">loba igcwalise isisu sayo ngomoya otshisayo wempumalanga na?<verse eid="JOB 15:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 15:3"/>Ingadaza inkani ngamazwi angatsho lutho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:3">ngezinkulumo ezingelasisindo na?<verse eid="JOB 15:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 15:4"/>Wena uze weyise ukulunga</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:4">njalo uphazame lokukhonza uNkulunkulu.<verse eid="JOB 15:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 15:5"/>Isono sakho sikhuthaza umlomo wakho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:5">usuthethe ulimi lwamaqili.<verse eid="JOB 15:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 15:6"/>Umlomo wakho yiwo okulahlayo, hatshi owami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:6">izindebe zakho zifakaza ububi bakho.<verse eid="JOB 15:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 15:7"/>Nguwe yini umuntu wokuqala ukuzalwa?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:7">Wabakhona kuqala kulezintaba na?<verse eid="JOB 15:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 15:8"/>Uyake ulalele yini enkundleni kaNkulunkulu?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:8">Nguwe wedwa yini ololwazi?<verse eid="JOB 15:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 15:9"/>Kuyini okwaziyo wena thina esingakwaziyo?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:9">Ulemibono bani wena thina esingelayo?<verse eid="JOB 15:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 15:10"/>Asebezimpunga lamakhehla bavumelana lathi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:10">amadoda amadala kuloyihlo.<verse eid="JOB 15:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 15:11"/>Induduzo zikaNkulunkulu kazikwanelisi yini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:11">amazwi akhulunywa kamnandi kuwe?<verse eid="JOB 15:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 15:12"/>Kungani uvumela ukufuqwa yinhliziyo na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:12">kungani amehlo akho eqwayiza,<verse eid="JOB 15:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 15:13"/>uze ubhodlise ulaka lwakho kuNkulunkulu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:13">ukhihlize amazwi anjalo ngomlomo wakho?<verse eid="JOB 15:13"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 15:14"/>Umuntu uyini ukuthi abe ngohlanzekileyo na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:14">lozelwe ngowesifazane ongaba ngcwele?<verse eid="JOB 15:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 15:15"/>Nxa uNkulunkulu engazethembi izingilosi zakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:15">njalo lamazulu engathembekanga kuye,<verse eid="JOB 15:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 15:16"/>pho umuntu ongcolileyo ke, oxhwalileyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:16">onatha ububi njengamanzi!<verse eid="JOB 15:16"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 15:17"/>Lalela kimi ngikuchazele;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:17">wothi ngikutshele esengakubonayo,<verse eid="JOB 15:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 15:18"/>lokho osekwafakazwa yizihlakaniphi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:18">bengafihli lutho abaluthatha kubokhokho babo<verse eid="JOB 15:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 15:19"/>(abayibo kuphela abaphiwa ilizwe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:19">njalo akwaze kwedlula muntu wezizweni phakathi kwabo):<verse eid="JOB 15:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 15:20"/>Ngezinsuku zakhe zonke umuntu omubi uhlutshwa yizinhlungu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:20">kube yisihluku seminyaka yonke ayibekelweyo.<verse eid="JOB 15:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 15:21"/>Imisindo eyesabisayo iyagcwala ezindlebeni zakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:21">nxa kusithi kuyalunga, izikliwi zimhlasele.<verse eid="JOB 15:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 15:22"/>Ulahlekelwa lithemba lokuwuphepha umnyama;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:22">umiselwe inkemba.<verse eid="JOB 15:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 15:23"/>Uyantula nje abe yikudla kwamanqe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:23">uyazi ukuthi usuku lobumnyama selusondele.<verse eid="JOB 15:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 15:24"/>Usizi lobuhlungu emoyeni bumlethela uvalo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:24">inhlupho ziyamgabhela, njengenkosi isilungele ukuhlasela,<verse eid="JOB 15:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 15:25"/>ngoba efumbathele uNkulunkulu inqindi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:25">ezimisela ukulwa loSomandla,<verse eid="JOB 15:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 15:26"/>aqholoze amhlasele</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:26">ngesihlangu esiqinileyo, esilohlonzi.<verse eid="JOB 15:26"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 15:27"/>Lanxa ezimuke ubuso bungaka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:27">umkhaba ulenga ngedanga,<verse eid="JOB 15:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 15:28"/>uzahlala emadolobheni angamanxiwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:28">lezindlini ezingahlali muntu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:28">izindlu eziwohlokayo zibe yinqumbi.<verse eid="JOB 15:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOB 15:29"/>Kasayikunotha futhi lenotho yakhe kayiyikuma,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:29">lezifuyo zakhe kazisayikugcwala ilizwe lonke.<verse eid="JOB 15:29"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOB 15:30"/>Kayikuphepha emnyameni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:30">ilangabi lizabunisa amahlumela akhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:30">lomoya wokuphefumula komlomo kaNkulunkulu uzamthwalela kude.<verse eid="JOB 15:30"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOB 15:31"/>Makangazikhohlisi ngokuthemba okuyize,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:31">ngoba akazukuzuza lutho ngakho.<verse eid="JOB 15:31"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOB 15:32"/>Singakapheli isikhathi sakhe uzajeziswa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:32">lezingatsha zakhe kaziyikuhluma.<verse eid="JOB 15:32"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOB 15:33"/>Uzaba njengevini eliphundlwe izithelo zalo zingakavuthwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:33">njengesihlahla se-oliva sikhithiza impoko zaso.<verse eid="JOB 15:33"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="JOB 15:34"/>Ngoba ixuku labangamesabiyo uNkulunkulu kalizukuba lezithelo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:34">lomlilo uzawahangula amathente alabo abathanda isivalamlomo.<verse eid="JOB 15:34"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="JOB 15:35"/>Bazithwala uhlupho babelethe ububi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 15:35">isibeletho sabo sibumba inkohliso.”<verse eid="JOB 15:35"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 15"/>
  <chapter number="16" style="c" sid="JOB 16"/>
  <para style="s1">UJobe Uyaphendula</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 16:1"/>UJobe wasephendula wathi:<verse eid="JOB 16:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 16:2"/>“Sengezwa izinto ezinengi ezifana lalezi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:2">lingabaduduzi ababi lina lonke!<verse eid="JOB 16:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 16:3"/>Zizaphela nini inkulumo zokubhuda kwenu lokhu?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:3">Kuyini okulihluphayo laphikelela nje lidaza inkani?<verse eid="JOB 16:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 16:4"/>Lami bengingakhuluma njengani</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:4">aluba yini elisesikhundleni sami;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 16:4">ngabe ngikhupha inkulumo ezimnandi ngilisola</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:4">ngize nginikine ikhanda lami.<verse eid="JOB 16:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 16:5"/>Kodwa umlomo wami ngabe uyaliqinisa;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:5">induduzo yezindebe zami idedise inhlungu zenu.<verse eid="JOB 16:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 16:6"/>Kodwa nxa ngikhuluma, ubuhlungu obukimi kabudedi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:6">loba ngingaze ngithule, kabupheli.<verse eid="JOB 16:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 16:7"/>Ngeqiniso, Nkulunkulu, usungiqede amandla;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:7">usuyitshabalalisile yonke imuli yami.<verse eid="JOB 16:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 16:8"/>Usungibophile sekuyibo ubufakazi balokho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:8">lokucikizeka kwami kuyakhula kungilahla.<verse eid="JOB 16:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 16:9"/>UNkulunkulu uyanginxwanela angidlikize ngolaka lwakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:9">angigedlele amazinyo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:9">isitha sami singinyonkoloze ngamehlo ahlabayo.<verse eid="JOB 16:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 16:10"/>Abantu bavula imilomo yabo bengihoza;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:10">bangimakala esihlathini bengihlambaza</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:10">babambane bangihlanganyele.<verse eid="JOB 16:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 16:11"/>UNkulunkulu usenginikele ebantwini ababi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:11">wangiphosela ezandleni zezigangi.<verse eid="JOB 16:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 16:12"/>Konke kwakukuhle kimi, kodwa wangibhidliza;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:12">wangixhakalaza ngentamo wangichoboza.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 16:12">Usengenze ngaba yinto yakhe yokunenjwa;<verse eid="JOB 16:12"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 16:13"/>abacibi bemtshoko bakhe bangihanqile.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 16:13">Ungiciba izinso zami engelazwelo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:13">achithele inyongo yami phansi.<verse eid="JOB 16:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 16:14"/>Ungisukela njalonjalo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:14">angidumele njengebutho.<verse eid="JOB 16:14"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 16:15"/>Sengithungele isembatho sesaka emzimbeni wami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:15">ngathukuza ibunzi lami othulini.<verse eid="JOB 16:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 16:16"/>Ubuso bami sebubomvu ngokukhala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:16">amathunzi anzima ahonqolozela amehlo ami;<verse eid="JOB 16:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 16:17"/>kodwa izandla zami kaziluqhelanga udlakela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:17">lomkhuleko wami uhlanzekile.<verse eid="JOB 16:17"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 16:18"/>Awu mhlaba, ungaligqibeli igazi lami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:18">sengathi lokukhala kwami kungaze kwacitshwa lanini!<verse eid="JOB 16:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 16:19"/>Lakhathesi ufakazi wami usezulwini;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:19">umeli wami uphezulu khonale.<verse eid="JOB 16:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 16:20"/>Umeli wami ngumngane wami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:20">nxa amehlo ami empompoza inyembezi kuNkulunkulu;<verse eid="JOB 16:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 16:21"/>uyamncengela umuntu kuNkulunkulu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:21">njengomuntu encengela umngane wakhe.<verse eid="JOB 16:21"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 16:22"/>Kusasele iminyakana engemingaki</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:22">andubana ngiye lapho kungabuywa khona.”<verse eid="JOB 16:22"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 16"/>
  <chapter number="17" style="c" sid="JOB 17"/>
  <para style="s1">UJobe Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 17:1"/>“Umoya wami udabukile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:1">insuku zami ziqunyiwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:1">ithuna lingimelele.<verse eid="JOB 17:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 17:2"/>Impela abaklolodayo bangihanqile;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:2">amehlo ami asehlezi elinde ulaka lwabo.<verse eid="JOB 17:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 17:3"/>Ngipha, Oh Nkulunkulu, lesosibambiso osifunayo.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:3">Kambe ngubani omunye ongangenzela lesosibambiso na?<verse eid="JOB 17:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 17:4"/>Usuzivalile ingqondo zabo kabasazwisisi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:4">ngakho kawuzukubayekela bagiye.<verse eid="JOB 17:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 17:5"/>Nxa umuntu angaphika umngane wakhe ukuze ahlawulwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:5">amehlo abantwabakhe azafiphala.<verse eid="JOB 17:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 17:6"/>UNkulunkulu usengenze ngaba yisiga ebantwini bonke,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:6">umuntu okhafulelwa ngabanye emehlweni.<verse eid="JOB 17:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 17:7"/>Amehlo ami asethundubele ngosizi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:7">umdumbu wami wonke usuyisithunzi nje.<verse eid="JOB 17:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 17:8"/>Abantu abaqotho kuyabanenga lokhu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:8">abangelacala bayacaphuka ngabangakholwayo.<verse eid="JOB 17:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 17:9"/>Kungenani, abalungileyo bazabambelela ezindleleni zabo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:9">kuthi labo abalezandla ezihlanzekileyo baqine.<verse eid="JOB 17:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 17:10"/>Kodwa khathesi lina lonke ake lizame futhi!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:10">Kangiboni loyedwa ohlakaniphileyo kini.<verse eid="JOB 17:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 17:11"/>Sezidlule insuku zami, amacebo ami asedilikile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:11">kunjalo lezifiso zenhliziyo yami.<verse eid="JOB 17:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 17:12"/>Lababantu bathatha ubusuku njengemini;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:12">bathi bebona ubumnyama bathi, ‘Ukukhanya sekusondele.’<verse eid="JOB 17:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 17:13"/>Nxa ikhaya engilithembileyo lilingcwaba kuphela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:13">nxa ngisendlala umbheda wami emnyameni,<verse eid="JOB 17:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 17:14"/>nxa ngisithi ekuboleni, ‘Baba,’</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:14">ngithi empethwini, ‘Mama’ kumbe ‘Dadewethu,’<verse eid="JOB 17:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 17:15"/>pho lingaphi ithemba lami na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:15">Ngubani ongabona ithemba ngami?<verse eid="JOB 17:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 17:16"/>Kuzakwehlela emasangweni okufa na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 17:16">Sizakwehlela ndawonye othulini na?”<verse eid="JOB 17:16"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 17"/>
  <chapter number="18" style="c" sid="JOB 18"/>
  <para style="s1">Impendulo KaBhilidadi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 18:1"/>Kwathi lapho uBhilidadi umShuhi waphendula wathi:<verse eid="JOB 18:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 18:2"/>“Koze kube nini ulokhu uphethe emlonyeni?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:2">Nakana andubana sikhulume.<verse eid="JOB 18:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 18:3"/>Kungani usithatha njengezinkomo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:3">kube ingathi siyizithutha kuwe na?<verse eid="JOB 18:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 18:4"/>Wena ozidabudabulayo ube yiziqa ngokuthukuthela kwakho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:4">uthi sesingawudela umhlaba ngenxa yakho?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:4">Loba uthi amadwala agudlulwe ezindaweni zawo na?<verse eid="JOB 18:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 18:5"/>Isibane somubi siyacima;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:5">ilangabi lomlilo wakhe liyaphela ukubhebha.<verse eid="JOB 18:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 18:6"/>Ukukhanya ethenteni lakhe kuyafiphala;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:6">isibane esiseceleni kwakhe siyacima.<verse eid="JOB 18:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 18:7"/>Izisinde zakhe zamandla ziyadeda;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:7">lamacebo akhe yiwo amlahla phansi.<verse eid="JOB 18:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 18:8"/>Inyawo zakhe zimbeka emambuleni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:8">acine esemthandele.<verse eid="JOB 18:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 18:9"/>Umjibila umhwiphula ngesithende;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:9">isihitshela simuthi nki.<verse eid="JOB 18:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 18:10"/>Isihitshela usifihlelwe phansi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:10">umjibila uthukuziwe endleleni yakhe.<verse eid="JOB 18:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 18:11"/>Uyethuka ngokwesaba inxa zonke</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:11">kumlandelele langaphi aya khona.<verse eid="JOB 18:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 18:12"/>Umonakalo umlambele;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:12">incithakalo imlindele nxa esiwa.<verse eid="JOB 18:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 18:13"/>Kudla ingxenye yesikhumba sakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:13">izibulo lokufa lidla izitho zakhe.<verse eid="JOB 18:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 18:14"/>Uyasuswa ekuvikelekeni kwethente lakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:14">aqhutshwe asiwe enkosini yokwesaba.<verse eid="JOB 18:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 18:15"/>Umlilo uhlala ethenteni lakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:15">isolufa evuthayo ichithachithwe emzini wakhe.<verse eid="JOB 18:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 18:16"/>Impande zakhe ziyabuna ngaphansi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:16">lamagatsha akhe abune ngaphezulu.<verse eid="JOB 18:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 18:17"/>Ukukhunjulwa kwakhe kuyaphela emhlabeni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:17">kalabizo elizweni.<verse eid="JOB 18:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 18:18"/>Uyasuswa ekukhanyeni aye ebumnyameni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:18">njalo axotshwe emhlabeni.<verse eid="JOB 18:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 18:19"/>Kalabantwana loba isizukulwane ebantwini bakibo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:19">kakho loyedwa owakhe lapho ake ahlala khona.<verse eid="JOB 18:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 18:20"/>Abantu bentshonalanga bayanengwa yisiphetho sakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:20">abantu bempumalanga bayatshaqeka.<verse eid="JOB 18:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 18:21"/>Ngempela linjalo ikhaya lomuntu omubi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 18:21">yiyo indawo yalowo ongamaziyo uNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="JOB 18:21"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 18"/>
  <chapter number="19" style="c" sid="JOB 19"/>
  <para style="s1">Impendulo KaJobe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 19:1"/>Wasephendula uJobe wathi:<verse eid="JOB 19:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 19:2"/>“Koze kube nini lilokhu lingichukuluza,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:2">lingicobodisa ngamazwi na?<verse eid="JOB 19:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 19:3"/>Selingithethise amahlandla alitshumi manje;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:3">lingihlasela lingelanhloni.<verse eid="JOB 19:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 19:4"/>Nxa kuliqiniso ukuthi ngiphambukile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:4">isiphambeko sami ngumlandu wami ngedwa.<verse eid="JOB 19:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 19:5"/>Nxa isibili liziphakamisa ngaphezulu kwami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:5">lingincindezele ngokuyangeka kwami,<verse eid="JOB 19:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 19:6"/>yazini ukuthi uNkulunkulu ungonile</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:6">wangithandela ngomambule wakhe.<verse eid="JOB 19:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 19:7"/>Loba ngingaze ngikhale ngithi, ‘Ngiyahlukuluzwa bo!’</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:7">angitholi mpendulo;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 19:7">loba ngicela uncedo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:7">kangahlulelwa ngokulunga.<verse eid="JOB 19:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 19:8"/>Uyivalile indlela yami akudluleki;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:8">izindlela zami uzembese ngomnyama.<verse eid="JOB 19:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 19:9"/>Usengiphucile konke ukuhlonitshwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:9">wangethula umqhele ekhanda lami.<verse eid="JOB 19:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 19:10"/>Ungidabula inxa zonke ngize ngiphele du;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:10">usiphuna ithemba lami njengesihlahla.<verse eid="JOB 19:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 19:11"/>Ulaka lwakhe luyavutha kimi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:11">ungibalela phakathi kwezitha zakhe.<verse eid="JOB 19:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 19:12"/>Amabutho akhe eza ngamandla;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:12">angakhela isihonqo sokungivimbezela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:12">amise egqagqele ithente lami.<verse eid="JOB 19:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 19:13"/>Usenze abafowethu bangihlamuka;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:13">abangane bami sebemelana lami.<verse eid="JOB 19:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 19:14"/>Izihlobo zami sezihambile;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:14">abangane bami sebekhohliwe ngami.<verse eid="JOB 19:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 19:15"/>Izethekeli zami lezincekukazi zami zithi ngingowemzini;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:15">zingikhangela njengowezizweni.<verse eid="JOB 19:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 19:16"/>Ngithi nxa ngibiza isisebenzi sami singasabeli,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:16">lokuba ngisincenga ngomlomo wami.<verse eid="JOB 19:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 19:17"/>Ukuphefumula kwami kuyamnukela umkami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:17">ngiyenyanyeka kubafowethu.<verse eid="JOB 19:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 19:18"/>Labafanyana bayangiklolodela;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:18">ngithi nxa ngiqhamuka bangihoze.<verse eid="JOB 19:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 19:19"/>Bonke abangane bami abasekhwapheni bayanengeka ngami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:19">labo engibathandayo sebengifulathele.<verse eid="JOB 19:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 19:20"/>Angiselalutho ngaphandle kwesikhumba lamathambo kuphela;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:20">ngiphephe manayinayi.<verse eid="JOB 19:20"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 19:21"/>Ngizwelani usizi, bangane bami, wobani losizi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:21">ngoba isandla sikaNkulunkulu singitshayile.<verse eid="JOB 19:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 19:22"/>Lingilandelelani njengoNkulunkulu na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:22">Lizakufa lasutha ngenyama yami na?<verse eid="JOB 19:22"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 19:23"/>Oh, uthi ngabe amazwi ami ayalotshwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:23">ngabe abhaliwe emqulwini,<verse eid="JOB 19:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 19:24"/>ngabe athwetshulwe ngensimbi phezu komnuso,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:24">loba agujwe edwaleni lanininini!<verse eid="JOB 19:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 19:25"/>Ngiyazi ukuthi uMhlengi wami uyaphila,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:25">lokuthi ekupheleni uzakuma emhlabeni.<verse eid="JOB 19:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 19:26"/>Kuzakuthi nxa isikhumba sami sesibhujisiwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:26">kodwa ngikuyo inyama yami ngizambona uNkulunkulu;<verse eid="JOB 19:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 19:27"/>mina ngokwami ngizambona ngawami amehlo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:27">mina hatshi omunye.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:27">Inhliziyo yami iyagubhazela ngokulangatha!<verse eid="JOB 19:27"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 19:28"/>Lingaze lithi, ‘Sizamzingela qho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:28">ngoba nguye ozilethele ukuhlupheka,’<verse eid="JOB 19:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOB 19:29"/>yini okumele liyesabe inkemba;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:29">ngoba intukuthelo izaletha isijeziso ngenkemba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 19:29">lapho-ke lizakwazi ukuthi kulokwahlulela.”<verse eid="JOB 19:29"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 19"/>
  <chapter number="20" style="c" sid="JOB 20"/>
  <para style="s1">Impendulo KaZofari</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 20:1"/>Wasephendula uZofari umNahama wathi:<verse eid="JOB 20:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 20:2"/>“Imicabango yami ekhathazekileyo ingifuqa ukuthi ngiphendule</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:2">ngoba sengikhubekile kakhulu.<verse eid="JOB 20:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 20:3"/>Ngizwa kulokukhuzwa okungilulazisayo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:3">njalo ukuzwisisa kwami kungifuqela ukuthi ngiphendule.<verse eid="JOB 20:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 20:4"/>Ngempela uyakwazi ukuthi kwakuvele kunjani lendulo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:4">kusukela ukubekwa komuntu emhlabeni,<verse eid="JOB 20:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 20:5"/>ukuthi injabulo yomubi imfitshane,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:5">intokozo yongakholwayo ngeyomzuzwana nje.<verse eid="JOB 20:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 20:6"/>Loba ukuzigqaja kwakhe kufika emazulwini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:6">lekhanda lakhe lithinta emayezini,<verse eid="JOB 20:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 20:7"/>uzabhubha okwaphakade, njengobulongwe bakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:7">labo abake bambona bazakuthi, ‘Ungaphi kanti?’<verse eid="JOB 20:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 20:8"/>Njengephupho uyanyamalala angabe esabonwa njalo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:8">axotshwe njengombono webusuku.<verse eid="JOB 20:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 20:9"/>Ilihlo elake lambona kalisayikumbona njalo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:9">indawo yakhe ingeke ibe isambona.<verse eid="JOB 20:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 20:10"/>Abantwabakhe bazazincengela ebayangeni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:10">ngezandla zakhe abuyisele inotho yakhe.<verse eid="JOB 20:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 20:11"/>Amadlabuzane obutsha alawo emathanjeni akhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:11">azalala kanye laye othulini.<verse eid="JOB 20:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 20:12"/>Loba ububi bumnandi emlonyeni wakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:12">ebufihla ngaphansi kolimi lwakhe,<verse eid="JOB 20:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 20:13"/>loba esehluleka ukutshiyana labo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:13">abugcine emlonyeni wakhe,<verse eid="JOB 20:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 20:14"/>kodwa ukudla kwakhe kuzahloba esiswini sakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:14">kuzaphenduka kube yibuhlungu bezinyoka ngaphakathi kwakhe.<verse eid="JOB 20:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 20:15"/>Uzayihlanza yonke inotho ayiginyayo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:15">uNkulunkulu uzakwenza isisu sakhe sikuhlanze konke.<verse eid="JOB 20:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 20:16"/>Uzamunya ubuhlungu bezinyoka;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:16">amazinyo ebululu azambulala.<verse eid="JOB 20:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 20:17"/>Akayikuyikholisa imifula,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:17">leyomifula egeleza uluju lolaza.<verse eid="JOB 20:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 20:18"/>Lokho akuginqeleyo kumele akubuyise engakudlanga;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:18">akayikuyikholisa inzuzo yokuthengiselana kwakhe.<verse eid="JOB 20:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 20:19"/>Ngoba ubebancindezela abayanga basala bengelalutho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:19">wathumba izindlu angazakhanga.<verse eid="JOB 20:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 20:20"/>Ngempela akayikudeda kulobubuhwaba bakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:20">ngeke azisindise ngenotho yakhe.<verse eid="JOB 20:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 20:21"/>Akusela lutho angabe esaludla;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:21">ukuphumelela kwakhe kakuyikuma.<verse eid="JOB 20:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 20:22"/>Phakathi kwenotho yakhe uzahlaselwa zinhlupho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:22">ubuhlungu buzamehlela ngamandla.<verse eid="JOB 20:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 20:23"/>Nxa esesigcwalisile isisu sakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:23">uNkulunkulu uzabhodlisela ulaka lwakhe oluvuthayo kuye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:23">akhwele ehle ngezidutshulo phezu kwakhe.<verse eid="JOB 20:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 20:24"/>Lanxa angaze abalekele isikhali sensimbi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:24">umtshoko wethusi uzamciba.<verse eid="JOB 20:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 20:25"/>Uyawuhwatsha emhlane wakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:25">umcijo wawo ocazimulayo awuhwatshe esibindini.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 20:25">Uzangenwa yikwesaba okukhulu;<verse eid="JOB 20:25"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 20:26"/>umnyama omkhulu uyilindele inotho yakhe.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 20:26">Umlilo ongungumayo uzamqeda</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:26">utshise lokho okuseleyo ethenteni lakhe.<verse eid="JOB 20:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 20:27"/>Amazulu azabembula ububi bakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:27">umhlaba uzamvukela.<verse eid="JOB 20:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 20:28"/>Isikhukhula sizayithwala indlu yakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:28">kungamanzi azimpophoma mhla wosuku lolaka lukaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="JOB 20:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOB 20:29"/>Sinjalo isiphetho uNkulunkulu asimisele ababi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 20:29">ilifa abalikhethelwe nguNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="JOB 20:29"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 20"/>
  <chapter number="21" style="c" sid="JOB 21"/>
  <para style="s1">UJobe Uyaphendula</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 21:1"/>UJobe wasephendula wathi:<verse eid="JOB 21:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 21:2"/>“Lalelani kuhle amazwi ami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:2">lokhu akube yinduduzo elingipha yona.<verse eid="JOB 21:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 21:3"/>Ake lingibekezelele nxa ngisakhuluma,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:3">ngithi nxa sengikhulumile liklolode.<verse eid="JOB 21:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 21:4"/>Ukusola kwami kuqonde umuntu yini?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:4">Ngingayekelelani ukucunuka pho?<verse eid="JOB 21:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 21:5"/>Ngikhangelani, lizamangala;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:5">vulani imilomo yenu ngezandla.<verse eid="JOB 21:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 21:6"/>Nxa ngikhumbula ngalokhu ngitshaywa luvalo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:6">ngizwa umzimba wami uqhaqhazela.<verse eid="JOB 21:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 21:7"/>Kungani ababi bephila impilo ende,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:7">baluphale nje amandla abo esanda?<verse eid="JOB 21:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 21:8"/>Babona abantwababo bezinza benamile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:8">inzalo yabo layo beyikhangele.<verse eid="JOB 21:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 21:9"/>Imizi yabo ihlezi kayilakwesaba;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:9">induku kaNkulunkulu kayikho phezu kwabo.<verse eid="JOB 21:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 21:10"/>Inkunzi zabo zikhuthele ziyazala;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:10">amankomokazi abo azala kuhle kawaphunzi.<verse eid="JOB 21:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 21:11"/>Abantwababo bayazihambela njengomhlambi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:11">izingane zabo ziyazigidela zichelesile.<verse eid="JOB 21:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 21:12"/>Bayahlabela betshaya izigubhu lamachacho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:12">bayazithokozisa ngomsindo wemiqangala.<verse eid="JOB 21:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 21:13"/>Yonke iminyaka yabo ngeyokuphumelela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:13">baze bayongena egodini belokuthula.<verse eid="JOB 21:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 21:14"/>Kodwa bathi kuNkulunkulu, ‘Tshiyana lathi!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:14">Kasifisi ukuzazi izindlela zakho.<verse eid="JOB 21:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 21:15"/>Ungubani yena uSomandla ofuna ukuthi simkhonze na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:15">Sizazuzani nxa sikhuleka kuye na?’<verse eid="JOB 21:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 21:16"/>Kodwa ukuphumelela kwabo kakukho ezandleni zabo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:16">ngakho kangisondeli ezelulekweni zababi.<verse eid="JOB 21:16"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 21:17"/>Kodwa kukangaki na isibane sababi sicinywa?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:17">Kukangaki besehlelwa ngamabhadi na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:17">abawabelwa nguNkulunkulu ezondile?<verse eid="JOB 21:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 21:18"/>Kukangaki besiba njengomule emoyeni na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:18">njengamakhoba ephetshulwa yisivunguzane?<verse eid="JOB 21:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 21:19"/>Kuthiwa, ‘UNkulunkulu ulomba isijeziso somuntu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:19">asibekele amadodana akhe.’</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 21:19">Kajezise yena umuntu ngokwakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:19">ukuze akwazi!<verse eid="JOB 21:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 21:20"/>Amehlo akhe kawakubone</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:20">ukuchithwa kwakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:20">kalunathe ulaka lukaSomandla.<verse eid="JOB 21:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 21:21"/>Ngoba uvele uzihlupha ngani ngemuli avele ezayitshiya</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:21">nxa izinyanga zakhe azabelweyo seziphelile na?<verse eid="JOB 21:21"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 21:22"/>Kambe ukhona ongafundisa uNkulunkulu ulwazi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:22">njengoba yena esahlulela labaphezulu na?<verse eid="JOB 21:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 21:23"/>Umuntu uyafa ephilile kuhle,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:23">kukuhle konke ekhululekile,<verse eid="JOB 21:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 21:24"/>umzimba wakhe uzimukile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:24">amathambo akhe egcwele umnkantsho.<verse eid="JOB 21:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 21:25"/>Omunye ufa elobuhlungu emphefumulweni wakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:25">evele engakaze akholise lutho oluhle.<verse eid="JOB 21:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 21:26"/>Bobabili balaliswe ndawonye eceleni komunye othulini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:26">impethu zinyakaze phezu kwabo bobabili.<verse eid="JOB 21:26"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 21:27"/>Ngiyazi kamhlophe ukuthi licabangani,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:27">amacebo elidinga ukungilimaza ngawo.<verse eid="JOB 21:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 21:28"/>Lithi, ‘Ingaphi-ke manje indlu yesikhulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:28">amathente okwakuhlala kuwo abantu ababi?’<verse eid="JOB 21:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOB 21:29"/>Kalikaze libuze labo abahambayo na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:29">Kalize lananzelela izinto abazilandisayo,<verse eid="JOB 21:29"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOB 21:30"/>ukuthi umuntu omubi uyaphepha ngosuku lokubhujiswa na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:30">ukuthi uyakhululwa ngosuku lwesiphithiphithi?<verse eid="JOB 21:30"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOB 21:31"/>Kambe ngubani omtshela ngobubi bakhe ebusweni bakhe na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:31">Ngubani ophindiselayo ngalokho akwenzileyo na?<verse eid="JOB 21:31"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOB 21:32"/>Uthwalelwa engcwabeni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:32">lilindwe ingcwaba lakhe ngemfanelo.<verse eid="JOB 21:32"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOB 21:33"/>Inhlabathi esigodini leso imnandi kuye;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:33">bonke abantu bayamlandela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:33">banengi kakhulu njalo abahamba kuqala kulaye.<verse eid="JOB 21:33"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="JOB 21:34"/>Pho-ke lingangiduduza njani likhuluma ize nje?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 21:34">Akusalanga lutho elilutshoyo ngaphandle kwenkohliso.”<verse eid="JOB 21:34"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 21"/>
  <chapter number="22" style="c" sid="JOB 22"/>
  <para style="s1">Impendulo Ka-Elifazi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 22:1"/>U-Elifazi umThemani wasephendula wathi:<verse eid="JOB 22:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 22:2"/>“Umuntu angasiza uNkulunkulu na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:2">Lesihlakaniphi uqobo kambe singamsiza na?<verse eid="JOB 22:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 22:3"/>Bekungamupha ntokozo bani uSomandla ukulunga kwakho na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:3">Ubengazuzani ngabe kuthiwa kawulasici na?<verse eid="JOB 22:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 22:4"/>Yikumesaba kwakho yini akukhuzela khona</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:4">lakwethesela khona amacala na?<verse eid="JOB 22:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 22:5"/>Kabubukhulu ububi bakho na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:5">Lezono zakho angithi kazipheli na?<verse eid="JOB 22:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 22:6"/>Wawubiza isibambiso kubafowenu kungelasizatho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:6">uhlubula abantu izigqoko zabo basale beze.<verse eid="JOB 22:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 22:7"/>Abakhatheleyo wawubancitsha amanzi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:7">abalambileyo ungabaphi ukudla,<verse eid="JOB 22:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 22:8"/>lanxa wena wawuyindoda elamandla, ulepulazi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:8">indoda ehlonitshwayo, uphila kulo.<verse eid="JOB 22:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 22:9"/>Abafelokazi wabaxotsha ungabaphanga lutho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:9">izintandane waziqeda amandla.<verse eid="JOB 22:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 22:10"/>Kungenxa yalokho usuhanqwe yimijibila,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:10">usuhlukuluzwa luhlupho masinyane,<verse eid="JOB 22:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 22:11"/>yikho kumnyama kangaka ungasaboni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:11">njalo yikho ususibekelwa zimpophoma zamanzi.<verse eid="JOB 22:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 22:12"/>UNkulunkulu kakho esiqongweni samazulu na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:12">Ake ubone phela ukuthi ziphakeme njani izinkanyezi ezisesiqongweni!<verse eid="JOB 22:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 22:13"/>Kodwa wena uthi, ‘UNkulunkulu wazini?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:13">Angahlulela phakathi komnyama onje?<verse eid="JOB 22:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 22:14"/>Usithwe ngamayezi amakhulu, ngakho kasiboni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:14">nxa ehambahamba ezulwini eliphezulu.’<verse eid="JOB 22:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 22:15"/>Wena-ke uzakwalela endleleni endala na</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:15">eseyahanjwa ngababi?<verse eid="JOB 22:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 22:16"/>Bedluliswa singakafiki isikhathi sabo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:16">izisekelo zabo zakhukhulwa nguzamcolo.<verse eid="JOB 22:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 22:17"/>Bathi kuNkulunkulu, ‘Tshiyana lathi!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:17">USomandla angasenzani na?’<verse eid="JOB 22:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 22:18"/>Ikanti kunguye owagcwalisa izindlu zabo ngezinto ezinhle,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:18">ngakho kangingeni ezelulekweni zababi.<verse eid="JOB 22:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 22:19"/>Abalungileyo bayakubona lokho bathokoze;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:19">abangelacala bayabahleka bathi,<verse eid="JOB 22:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 22:20"/>‘Ngempela izitha zethu zichithiwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:20">lokuseleyo kwenotho yazo sekubhuqwe ngumlilo.’<verse eid="JOB 22:20"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 22:21"/>Zehlise kuNkulunkulu ukuze uwelelane laye;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:21">ngaleyondlela ukuphumelela kuzakuza kuwe.<verse eid="JOB 22:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 22:22"/>Yamukela iziqondiso eziphuma emlonyeni wakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:22">amazwi akhe uwabeke enhliziyweni yakho.<verse eid="JOB 22:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 22:23"/>Nxa ubuyela kuSomandla, uzavuselelwa;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:23">nxa ususa ububi bube kude lethente lakho<verse eid="JOB 22:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 22:24"/>lomthuso wakho uwulahlele othulini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:24">igolide lakho lase-Ofiri ulilahlele emadwaleni ezifuleni,<verse eid="JOB 22:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 22:25"/>lapho-ke uSomandla uzakuba ligolide lakho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:25">lesiliva esikhethekileyo kuwe.<verse eid="JOB 22:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 22:26"/>Ngempela uzazuza ukuthokoza kuSomandla</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:26">uphakamisele ubuso bakho kuNkulunkulu.<verse eid="JOB 22:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 22:27"/>Uzakhuleka kuye, yena akuzwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:27">njalo uzagcwalisa izifungo zakho.<verse eid="JOB 22:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 22:28"/>Lokho okumisileyo kuzakwenziwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:28">lokukhanya kuzazikhanyisa izindlela zakho.<verse eid="JOB 22:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOB 22:29"/>Nxa abantu besehliswa ubususithi, ‘Baphakamiseni!’</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:29">lapho-ke uzabasiza abahlulukelweyo.<verse eid="JOB 22:29"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOB 22:30"/>Uzabasiza lalabo abonayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 22:30">abazakhululwa ngenxa yokubamsulwa kwakho.”<verse eid="JOB 22:30"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 22"/>
  <chapter number="23" style="c" sid="JOB 23"/>
  <para style="s1">UJobe Uyaphendula</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 23:1"/>Waphendula uJobe wathi:<verse eid="JOB 23:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 23:2"/>“Lalamuhla ukusola kwami kulokhu kubuhlungu kabi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:2">isandla sakhe siyasinda loba ngibubula kangaka.<verse eid="JOB 23:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 23:3"/>Ngabe ngiyakwazi lapho engingamfumana khona;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:3">aluba nje bengingaya emzini wakhe!<verse eid="JOB 23:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 23:4"/>Bengizayibeka kuhle indaba yami phambi kwakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:4">ngigcwalise umlomo wami ngamazwi empikiswano.<verse eid="JOB 23:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 23:5"/>Bengizakuzwa ukuthi yena uphendula athini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:5">ngikuhlolisise lokho akutshoyo.<verse eid="JOB 23:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 23:6"/>Kambe angangiphikisa ngamandla na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:6">Hatshi, angazake angethese cala.<verse eid="JOB 23:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 23:7"/>Lapho umuntu oqotho ubengendlala indaba yakhe phambi kwakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:7">njalo bengizakhululwa lanini kumahluleli wami.<verse eid="JOB 23:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 23:8"/>Kodwa nxa ngisiya empumalanga, yena kakho khona;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:8">nxa ngisiya entshonalanga, kangimfumani khona.<verse eid="JOB 23:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 23:9"/>Nxa esemsebenzini enyakatho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:9">kangimboni;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 23:9">angaphendukela eningizimu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:9">kangiboni lokuthi tshazi kwakhe.<verse eid="JOB 23:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 23:10"/>Kodwa uyayazi indlela engihamba ngayo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:10">nxa esengilingile, ngizaphuma senginjengegolide.<verse eid="JOB 23:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 23:11"/>Inyawo zami bezilokhu zilandelana lezinyathelo zakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:11">ngalela endleleni yakhe angaze ngaphambuka.<verse eid="JOB 23:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 23:12"/>Angigudlukanga emilayweni yezindebe zakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:12">ngiwenze igugu amazwi omlomo wakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:12">ukwedlula isinkwa sami sansukuzonke.<verse eid="JOB 23:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 23:13"/>Kodwa uzimele yedwa, ngubani ongaphikisana laye na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:13">Uyenza loba yini ayifunayo.<verse eid="JOB 23:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 23:14"/>Uyagcwalisa isimiso sakhe ngami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:14">njalo manengi amacebo anjalo awagcinileyo.<verse eid="JOB 23:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 23:15"/>Yikho-nje ngithuthumela ukuma phambi kwakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:15">ngithi ngingakukhumbula konke lokhu ngimesabe.<verse eid="JOB 23:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 23:16"/>UNkulunkulu usenze inhliziyo yami yaphela amandla;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:16">uSomandla usengethusile.<verse eid="JOB 23:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 23:17"/>Kodwa kawuyikungithulisa umnyama lo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 23:17">umnyama lo onzima ovala ubuso bami.”<verse eid="JOB 23:17"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="JOB 23"/>
  <chapter number="24" style="c" sid="JOB 24"/>
  <para style="s1">UJobe Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 24:1"/>“Kungani uSomandla engabeki izikhathi zokwahlulela na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:1">Kungani labo abamaziyo belindela ize bengazazi lezinsuku na?<verse eid="JOB 24:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 24:2"/>Abantu bayayiguqula imingcele ngokususa izikhonkwane;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:2">bayayelusa imihlambi entshontshiweyo.<verse eid="JOB 24:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 24:3"/>Bayathatha bahambe lobabhemi wentandane,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:3">bathathe inkabi yomfelokazi ibe yisibambiso.<verse eid="JOB 24:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 24:4"/>Abaswelayo bayabagudlula endleleni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:4">bancindezele abayanga belizweni baze bayocatsha.<verse eid="JOB 24:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 24:5"/>Njengabobabhemi beganga enkangala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:5">abayanga babhudula ukudla;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:5">egwaduleni kulapho okuzuzwa khona ukudla kwabantwababo.<verse eid="JOB 24:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 24:6"/>Babutha ukudla kwenkomo emasimini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:6">badobhe okuseleyo ezivinini zababi.<verse eid="JOB 24:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 24:7"/>Ngoba bengelazigqoko balala beze ubusuku bonke;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:7">kabalalutho lokuzembesa emqandweni.<verse eid="JOB 24:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 24:8"/>Bagxonxwa lizulu lezintabeni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:8">bakhusele emadwaleni beswele indawo yokuphephela.<verse eid="JOB 24:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 24:9"/>Umntwana oyintandane uhluthunwa ebeleni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:9">usane lomyanga luyathunjelwa isikwelede.<verse eid="JOB 24:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 24:10"/>Ngoba bengelazigqoko bahamba nqunu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:10">bathwala izikhwebu zamabele kodwa belambile.<verse eid="JOB 24:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 24:11"/>Bahluza ama-oliva emigelweni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:11">bagidagida esikhamelweni sewayini kodwa bomile.<verse eid="JOB 24:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 24:12"/>Ukububula kwabafayo kuzwakala kuphuma edolobheni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:12">lemiphefumulo yabalimeleyo ikhala icela uncedo.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:12">Kodwa uNkulunkulu kabeki muntu icala ngenxa yokona.<verse eid="JOB 24:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 24:13"/>Bakhona labo abahlamukela ukukhanya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:13">abangazaziyo izindlela zalokho kukhanya</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:13">loba ukuhlala kuzo.<verse eid="JOB 24:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 24:14"/>Nxa ukukhanya kwemini sekuhambile</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:14">isigebenga siyaphuma sibulale abampofu labaswelayo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:14">ebusuku siyanyonyoba njengesela.<verse eid="JOB 24:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 24:15"/>Ilihlo lesiphingi lilindela ukuhlwa;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:15">sikhumbula sithi, ‘Akulamuntu ozangibona,’</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:15">sihlala sibusithile ubuso baso.<verse eid="JOB 24:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 24:16"/>Ebumnyameni abantu bayagqekeza izindlu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:16">kodwa emini bayazivalela endlini;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:16">kabakufuni ukukhanya.<verse eid="JOB 24:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 24:17"/>Bonke labo ubumnyama obukhulu buyikusa kubo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:17">bathandana lezinto ezesabekayo ezobumnyama.<verse eid="JOB 24:17"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 24:18"/>Ikanti baligwebu phezu kwamanzi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:18">esabo isabelo selizwe siqalekisiwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:18">ukuze kungayi muntu ezivinini.<verse eid="JOB 24:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 24:19"/>Njengalokhu ukutshisa lokoma kuhangula ungqwaqwane oncibilikayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:19">kanjalo ingcwaba liyabahlwitha abenze isono.<verse eid="JOB 24:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 24:20"/>Isibeletho siyabakhohlwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:20">impethu zizitike phezu kwabo;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 24:20">abantu ababi kabasakhunjulwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:20">kodwa bayafohlozwa njengesihlahla.<verse eid="JOB 24:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 24:21"/>Bancindezela owesifazane oyinyumba longelamntwana,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:21">kumfelokazi kabalamusa.<verse eid="JOB 24:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 24:22"/>Kodwa uNkulunkulu uyazihudulela kude izikhulu ngamandla akhe.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:22">Noma bangaze bahlale bazinze kodwa kabalathemba lempilo.<verse eid="JOB 24:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 24:23"/>Angabayekela bahlale besizwa bevikelekile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:23">kodwa amehlo akhe ayazibona izindlela zabo.<verse eid="JOB 24:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 24:24"/>Okwesikhatshana nje balodumo, baphinde banyamalale;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:24">bayehliswa njalo bafe njengabo bonke abanye;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:24">bayaqunywa njengezihloko zamabele.<verse eid="JOB 24:24"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 24:25"/>Aluba lokhu kungenjalo, ngubani ongathi ngilamanga</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 24:25">alulazise amazwi ami abe yize?”<verse eid="JOB 24:25"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 24"/>
  <chapter number="25" style="c" sid="JOB 25"/>
  <para style="s1">UBhilidadi Uyaphendula</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 25:1"/>Kwathi-ke uBhilidadi umShuhi waphendula wathi:<verse eid="JOB 25:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 25:2"/>“Umbuso lesizotha kukuye uNkulunkulu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 25:2">nguye omisa konke ngemfanelo ezulwini eliphezulu.<verse eid="JOB 25:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 25:3"/>Amabutho akhe angabalwa na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 25:3">Ngubani ongaphunyelwa yikukhanya kwakhe na?<verse eid="JOB 25:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 25:4"/>Pho umuntu angaba ngolungileyo njani kuNkulunkulu na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 25:4">Angenza njani ozelwe ngowesifazane ukuthi ahlanzeke na?<verse eid="JOB 25:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 25:5"/>Khangela, nxa inyanga ngokwayo ingakhazimuli,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 25:5">lezinkanyezi zingahlanzekanga emehlweni akhe,<verse eid="JOB 25:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 25:6"/>pho umuntu-ke usilela kanganani, oyimpethu nje,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 25:6">umuntu, oyinhlava nje kuphela!”<verse eid="JOB 25:6"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 25"/>
  <chapter number="26" style="c" sid="JOB 26"/>
  <para style="s1">UJobe Uyaphendula</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 26:1"/>UJobe wasephendula wathi:<verse eid="JOB 26:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 26:2"/>“Usumsize njani ongelamandla!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 26:2">Usuyilamulele njani ingalo ebuthakathaka!<verse eid="JOB 26:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 26:3"/>Yiseluleko esinjani osusiphe lowo ongelakuhlakanipha!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 26:3">Njalo usubonise mbono bani!<verse eid="JOB 26:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 26:4"/>Ngubani okuncedisileyo ukukhuluma amazwi la na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 26:4">Ngokabani umoya okhulume ngomlomo wakho na?<verse eid="JOB 26:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 26:5"/>Abafileyo basebuhlungwini obukhulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 26:5">labo abangaphansi kwamanzi lalabo abahlala kuwo.<verse eid="JOB 26:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 26:6"/>UKufa kwambulekile phambi kukaNkulunkulu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 26:6">ikhamisile indawo yokubhubha.<verse eid="JOB 26:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 26:7"/>Uyawendlala umkhathi wenyakatho endaweni engelalutho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 26:7">aphanyeke umhlaba phezu kweze.<verse eid="JOB 26:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 26:8"/>Ugoqele amanzi emayezini akhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 26:8">kodwa amayezi kawapatshaki yikusindwa ngamanzi.<verse eid="JOB 26:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 26:9"/>Uyayigubuzela inyanga egcweleyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 26:9">endlale amayezi phezu kwayo.<verse eid="JOB 26:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 26:10"/>Umisa umkhawulo wokwengama umkhathi emanzini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 26:10">kube ngumngcele phakathi kokukhanya lobumnyama.<verse eid="JOB 26:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 26:11"/>Izinsika zamazulu ziyazamazama,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 26:11">zisethuswa yikukhuza kwakhe.<verse eid="JOB 26:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 26:12"/>Ngamandla akhe waluthulisa ulwandle;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 26:12">ngenhlakanipho yakhe waquma uRahabi waba yiziqa.<verse eid="JOB 26:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 26:13"/>Ngomoya wakhe umkhathi wacethula;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 26:13">isandla sakhe sayigwaza inyoka ibaleka.<verse eid="JOB 26:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 26:14"/>Njalo le yimisebenzi yakhe engaphandle nje ekucineni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 26:14">esikuzwayo yilizwana nje lokunyenyeza kwakhe!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 26:14">Pho ngubani ongawuzwisisa umdumo wamandla akhe na?”<verse eid="JOB 26:14"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 26"/>
  <chapter number="27" style="c" sid="JOB 27"/>
  <para style="s1">Amazwi KaJobe Okucina Ebanganini Bakhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 27:1"/>UJobe waqhubeka ngenkulumo yakhe wathi:<verse eid="JOB 27:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 27:2"/>“Ngifunga ngoNkulunkulu ophilayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:2">ngubani ongithathele ilungelo lami lokwahlulelwa ngokulunga,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:2">uSomandla, ongizwise ubuhlungu bomphefumulo,<verse eid="JOB 27:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 27:3"/>nxa ngilokhu ngiselempilo ngaphakathi kwami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:3">umphefumulo kaNkulunkulu usemakhaleni ami,<verse eid="JOB 27:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 27:4"/>izindebe zami kazisoze zikhulume ububi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:4">lolimi lwami kaluyikukhuluma inkohliso.<verse eid="JOB 27:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 27:5"/>Kangisoze ngivume ukuthi lina lilungile ngelikutshoyo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:5">ngizaze ngiyekufa ngingabulandulanga ubuqotho bami.<verse eid="JOB 27:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 27:6"/>Ngizakugcina ukulunga kwami ngingakuyekeli;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:6">umzwangedwa wami kawuyikungihlupha empilweni yami.<verse eid="JOB 27:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 27:7"/>Sengathi izitha zami zingaba njengababi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:7">abaxabana lami babe njengabangaqondanga!<verse eid="JOB 27:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 27:8"/>Ngoba ulethemba bani ongakholwayo nxa esefile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:8">uNkulunkulu angathatha impilo yakhe na?<verse eid="JOB 27:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 27:9"/>UNkulunkulu uyakulalela yini ukukhala kwakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:9">nxa usizi lumehlela na?<verse eid="JOB 27:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 27:10"/>Uzakuthola yini ukuthokoza kuSomandla?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:10">Uzacela kuNkulunkulu sonke isikhathi na?<verse eid="JOB 27:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 27:11"/>Ngizalifundisa mayelana lamandla kaNkulunkulu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:11">izindlela zikaSomandla kangiyikuzifihla.<verse eid="JOB 27:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 27:12"/>Lonke lizibonele lokhu ngokwenu.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:12">Pho, ngeyani inkulumo yonke le eyize na?<verse eid="JOB 27:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 27:13"/>Nansi isabelo uNkulunkulu asiqumela ababi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:13">ilifa elemukelwa ngumuntu olesihluku sivela kuSomandla:<verse eid="JOB 27:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 27:14"/>Loba bebanengi njani abantwabakhe, isabelo sabo yinkemba;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:14">lenzalo yakhe kayisoze lanini izuze ukudla okwaneleyo.<verse eid="JOB 27:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 27:15"/>Isifo esibi sizabangcwaba labo abatshiywa nguye besaphila,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:15">labafelokazi babo kabayikubalilela.<verse eid="JOB 27:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 27:16"/>Lokuba angaze abuthelele isiliva njengothuli</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:16">lezigqoko zibe yinqwaba njengodaka,<verse eid="JOB 27:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 27:17"/>lokho akubuthelelayo abalungileyo bazakugqokela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:17">labangelacala bazakwaba isiliva sakhe.<verse eid="JOB 27:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 27:18"/>Indlu ayakhayo injengesidleke sobulembu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:18">njengedumba elenziwe ngumlindi.<verse eid="JOB 27:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 27:19"/>Uthi esiyalala enothile, kodwa kasayikuphinda njalo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:19">uthi esevula amehlo, konke sekuphelile.<verse eid="JOB 27:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 27:20"/>Utshaywa luvalo kungathi ufuqwa yisikhukhula;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:20">isiphepho siyamhwitha ebusuku.<verse eid="JOB 27:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 27:21"/>Umoya wempumalanga udlula laye, anyamalale;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:21">uyamkhukhula endaweni yakhe.<verse eid="JOB 27:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 27:22"/>Utshaya phezu kwakhe ngesihluku</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:22">esithi uyabaleka ecambalele evika amandla awo.<verse eid="JOB 27:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 27:23"/>Utshaya izandla umhleka ulunya</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 27:23">uvunguza laye umsusa endaweni yakhe.”<verse eid="JOB 27:23"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 27"/>
  <chapter number="28" style="c" sid="JOB 28"/>
  <para style="s1">Lapho Okutholakala Khona Inhakanipho</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 28:1"/>Kulomgodi wesiliva</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:1">lendawo lapho okucengwa khona igolide.<verse eid="JOB 28:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 28:2"/>Insimbi ithathwa emhlabathini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:2">lethusi lincibilikiswa emanyeleni.<verse eid="JOB 28:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 28:3"/>Umuntu uyawuxotsha umnyama;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:3">uguduza ezingoxweni eziphansi kude</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:3">edinga amanyele emnyameni othe bhuqe.<verse eid="JOB 28:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 28:4"/>Khatshana kwezindawo zabantu ugebha umgodi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:4">ezindaweni lapho okungafiki nyawo lwamuntu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:4">khatshana kwabantu uyalenga, azunguzeke.<verse eid="JOB 28:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 28:5"/>Umhlaba, okuphuma kuwo ukudla,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:5">uyaguquka ngaphansi ingathi utshiswe ngomlilo;<verse eid="JOB 28:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 28:6"/>amasafire amatshe amahle ayaphuma emadwaleni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:6">uthuli lwawo lugcwele igolide.<verse eid="JOB 28:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 28:7"/>Kakukho nyoni edla inyama eyaziyo leyondlela efihlekileyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:7">kakulalihlo laluphi ukhozi oselwake lwayibona.<verse eid="JOB 28:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 28:8"/>Izilo ezizithembileyo kazilubeki unyawo kuyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:8">njalo kakulasilwane esizingela khona.<verse eid="JOB 28:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 28:9"/>Isandla somuntu yiso esihlasela idwala eliyinsengetshe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:9">siveze obala impande zezintaba.<verse eid="JOB 28:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 28:10"/>Uyaligubha idwala angene;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:10">ilihlo lakhe liwabone wonke amagugu alo.<verse eid="JOB 28:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 28:11"/>Uyathungatha lapho okudabuka khona imifula</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:11">aveze obala izinto ezifihlekileyo.<verse eid="JOB 28:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 28:12"/>Kodwa ukuhlakanipha kungafunyanwa ngaphi na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:12">Kuhlala ngaphi na ukuzwisisa?<verse eid="JOB 28:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 28:13"/>Umuntu kakuzwisisi ukuqakatheka kwakho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:13">kakufunyanwa elizweni labaphilayo.<verse eid="JOB 28:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 28:14"/>Phansi ekujuleni kuthi, “Kakukho kimi”;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:14">ulwandle luthi, “Kangilakho mina.”<verse eid="JOB 28:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 28:15"/>Kungeke kwathengwa ngegolide elicolekileyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:15">njalo lentengo yakho ingeke yalinganiswa ngesiliva.<verse eid="JOB 28:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 28:16"/>Kungeke kwathengwa ngegolide lase-Ofiri,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:16">loba nge-onikisi kumbe isafire.<verse eid="JOB 28:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 28:17"/>Kungazake kulinganiswe legolide loba amatshe akhazimulayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:17">njalo kakuzuzwa ngemiceciso yegolide.<verse eid="JOB 28:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 28:18"/>Amatshe amahle ekhorali lejaspa lawo kawabalwa lapha;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:18">intengo yokuhlakanipha ingaphezulu kwamarubhi.<verse eid="JOB 28:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 28:19"/>Ithophazi yaseKhushi ngeke ilinganiswe lakho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:19">ngeke kuthengwe langegolide elicolekileyo.<verse eid="JOB 28:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 28:20"/>Pho kuvela ngaphi ukuhlakanipha na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:20">Kuhlala ngaphi ukuzwisisa?<verse eid="JOB 28:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 28:21"/>Kufihliwe emehlweni ento yonke ephilayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:21">kucatshisiwe lakuzo izinyoni zasemoyeni.<verse eid="JOB 28:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 28:22"/>INcithakalo loKufa kuthi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:22">“Amahungahunga akho yiwo kuphela esiwezwayo.”<verse eid="JOB 28:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 28:23"/>UNkulunkulu uyayizwisisa indlela yakho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:23">njalo nguye yedwa okwaziyo lapho okuhlala khona,<verse eid="JOB 28:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 28:24"/>ngoba uyayikhangela imikhawulo yomhlaba</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:24">akubone konke okungaphansi kwamazulu.<verse eid="JOB 28:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 28:25"/>Wathi emisa umfutho womoya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:25">elinganisa isimo samanzi,<verse eid="JOB 28:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 28:26"/>wathi ebeka umthetho wezulu elinayo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:26">lendlela yezulu elilesiphepho,<verse eid="JOB 28:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 28:27"/>wasekukhangela ukuhlakanipha wakuhlola butsha;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:27">wakukholwa wakuqinisa, wakulinga ukuthi kuqinile.<verse eid="JOB 28:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 28:28"/>Wathi emuntwini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:28">“Ukumesaba uThixo yikho ukuhlakanipha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 28:28">lokuxwaya ububi yikho ukuzwisisa.”<verse eid="JOB 28:28"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 28"/>
  <chapter number="29" style="c" sid="JOB 29"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuzigeza KukaJobe Kokucina</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 29:1"/>UJobe waqhubeka ngenkulumo yakhe wathi:<verse eid="JOB 29:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 29:2"/>“Ngiyaziloyisa lezozinyanga esezadlulayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:2">lezinsuku uNkulunkulu esangilinda,<verse eid="JOB 29:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 29:3"/>lapho isibane sakhe sisakhanyisa phezu kwekhanda lami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:3">ngihamba ngokukhanya kwakhe emnyameni!<verse eid="JOB 29:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 29:4"/>Oh, lezinsuku ngisazizwa ukuthi ngiyimi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:4">lapho ubudlelwano obukhulu loNkulunkulu busesendlini yami,<verse eid="JOB 29:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 29:5"/>lapho uSomandla eseselami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:5">labantwabami besaphila lami,<verse eid="JOB 29:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 29:6"/>lapho indlela yami ifafazwe ngolaza ledwala</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:6">lingithululela impophoma zamafutha e-oliva.<verse eid="JOB 29:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 29:7"/>Ekuyeni kwami emasangweni edolobho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:7">ngafika ngahlala enkundleni,<verse eid="JOB 29:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 29:8"/>amajaha angibona agudluka ema eceleni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:8">abadala baphakama bema ngezinyawo;<verse eid="JOB 29:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 29:9"/>amadoda ayizikhulu athula akaze akhuluma</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:9">avala imilomo yawo ngezandla zawo;<verse eid="JOB 29:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 29:10"/>amazwi ezikhulu ehliselwa phansi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:10">inlimi zazo zanamathela olwangeni lwazo.<verse eid="JOB 29:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 29:11"/>Loba ngubani owangizwayo wakhuluma kuhle ngami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:11">kwathi labo abangibonayo bangibuka,<verse eid="JOB 29:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 29:12"/>ngoba ngalamulela abayanga abacela uncedo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:12">lezintandane ezazingelamsizi.<verse eid="JOB 29:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 29:13"/>Indoda eyayisifa yangibusisa;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:13">ngenza inhliziyo yomfelokazi yahlabelela.<verse eid="JOB 29:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 29:14"/>Ngavunula ukulunga njengezigqoko zami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:14">ukwahlulela ngokulunga kwaba yisembatho sami lengwane yami.<verse eid="JOB 29:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 29:15"/>Ngangingamehlo kwabayiziphofu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:15">lezinyawo kwabaqhulayo.<verse eid="JOB 29:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 29:16"/>Nganginguyise kwabaswelayo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:16">ngayimela indaba yesihambi.<verse eid="JOB 29:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 29:17"/>Ngawephula amazinyo ababi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:17">ngahluthuna labo ababebabambile ngamazinyo abo.<verse eid="JOB 29:17"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 29:18"/>Ngakhumbula ngathi, ‘Ngizafela endlini yami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:18">insuku zami zinengi njengezinhlamvu zetshebetshebe.<verse eid="JOB 29:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 29:19"/>Impande zami zizafinyelela emanzini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:19">amazolo azalala emagatsheni ubusuku bonke.<verse eid="JOB 29:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 29:20"/>Udumo lwami luzahlala lulutsha kimi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:20">idandili lami lilitsha esandleni sami.’<verse eid="JOB 29:20"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 29:21"/>Abantu babengilalela belethemba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:21">belindele ukwelulekwa bethule zwi.<verse eid="JOB 29:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 29:22"/>Nxa sekukhulume mina, kungakhulumi omunye njalo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:22">amazwi ami ayengena kamnandi ezindlebeni zabo.<verse eid="JOB 29:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 29:23"/>Babengilindela njengokulindela izulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:23">bawanathe amazwi ami njengezulu lentwasa.<verse eid="JOB 29:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 29:24"/>Ngangisithi ngingababobothekela, bathabe bangakholwa;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:24">ukukhanya kobuso bami kwakuligugu kubo.<verse eid="JOB 29:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 29:25"/>Yimi engangibakhethela ukuthi benzeni ngoba ngisanduna kubo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:25">ngangihlala njengenkosi phakathi kwamabutho ayo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 29:25">ngangifana lomduduzi wabalilayo.”<verse eid="JOB 29:25"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="JOB 29"/>
  <chapter number="30" style="c" sid="JOB 30"/>
  <para style="s1">UJobe Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 30:1"/>“Kodwa manje bayangiklolodela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:1">amadoda angabantwana kimi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 30:1">oyise engangingabehlisa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:1">ngibelusise izimvu zami.<verse eid="JOB 30:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 30:2"/>Amandla ezandla zabo ayengangisiza ngani mina,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:2">ngoba amadlabuzane abo ayesephelile;<verse eid="JOB 30:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 30:3"/>sebejujukile ngokuswela langendlala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:3">bazula elizweni elomileyo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:3">emangweni eyinkangala engelalutho ebusuku.<verse eid="JOB 30:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 30:4"/>Enkotheni khonale bakha imibhida emunyu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:4">ukudla kwabo kuzimpande zezihlahla.<verse eid="JOB 30:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 30:5"/>Baxotshwa ebantwini bakibo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:5">bathethiswa kungathi babengamasela.<verse eid="JOB 30:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 30:6"/>Kwasekumele bahlale ezihotsheni zezifula ezomileyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:6">ezimbalwini emadwaleni lemilindini emhlabathini.<verse eid="JOB 30:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 30:7"/>Bakhonya phakathi kwezihlahla</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:7">baququbala ezixukwini.<verse eid="JOB 30:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 30:8"/>Base bengabantu abaphansi abangaselabizo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:8">sebexotshiwe elizweni.<verse eid="JOB 30:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 30:9"/>Kodwa manje amadodana abo asengihaya ngengoma;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:9">sengiyisiga kubo.<verse eid="JOB 30:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 30:10"/>Bayangenyanya njalo bamela khatshana lami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:10">kabathikazi ukungikhafulela ebusweni.<verse eid="JOB 30:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 30:11"/>Khathesi njengoba uNkulunkulu eselithukulule idandili lami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:11">wangitshaya ngezinhlupheko,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:11">sebeklamasa kabasazithinti.<verse eid="JOB 30:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 30:12"/>Kwesokunene kwami ixuku liyangihlasela;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:12">bathiya inyawo zami ngemijibila</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:12">bakhe imibundu yokungivimbezela.<verse eid="JOB 30:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 30:13"/>Badiliza indlela yami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:13">bayaphumelela ukungibhidliza</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:13">besithi ‘Akekho ozamsiza.’<verse eid="JOB 30:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 30:14"/>Bahlasela ingathi bafohlela esikhaleni esivulekileyo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:14">beza bethululeka phezu kwezinqwaba zamanxiwa.<verse eid="JOB 30:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 30:15"/>Ukwesaba okukhulu kungiphethe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:15">isithunzi sami sobuntu singathi siphethwe ngumoya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:15">ukuvikeleka kwami kunyamalala njengeyezi.<verse eid="JOB 30:15"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 30:16"/>Manje impilo yami isincipha;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:16">insuku zokuhlupheka zingibambe nko.<verse eid="JOB 30:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 30:17"/>Ubusuku bugwaza amathambo ami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:17">lokuqaqamba kobuhlungu bami kakupheli.<verse eid="JOB 30:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 30:18"/>Ngamandla akhe amakhulu uNkulunkulu unjengelembu kimi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:18">uyangikhama ngamabheqe entanyeni yami.<verse eid="JOB 30:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 30:19"/>Ungivoxela edakeni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:19">ngicina sengiluthuli lomlotha.<verse eid="JOB 30:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 30:20"/>Ngikhala kuwe, Oh Nkulunkulu, kodwa kawuphenduli;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:20">ngiyasukuma, kodwa uyangikhangela kuphela.<verse eid="JOB 30:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 30:21"/>Ungisukela ngesihluku;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:21">ungihlasela ngamandla esandla sakho.<verse eid="JOB 30:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 30:22"/>Uyangihlwitha ngiphetshulwe ngumoya;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:22">ngiphoseke le lale phakathi kwesiphepho.<verse eid="JOB 30:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 30:23"/>Ngiyazi ukuthi uzangilalisa phansi ekufeni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:23">endaweni emiselwe konke okuphilayo.<verse eid="JOB 30:23"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 30:24"/>Ngempela kakho ombeka isandla umuntu oswelayo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:24">nxa ekhalela ukusizwa esebunzimeni.<verse eid="JOB 30:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 30:25"/>Kangibakhalelanga yini labo abahluphekileyo?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:25">Umoya wami kawubazwelanga usizi abayanga na?<verse eid="JOB 30:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 30:26"/>Kodwa ngathi ngilindele ubuhle, kweza ububi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:26">ngathi ngilindele ukukhanya kweza ubumnyama.<verse eid="JOB 30:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 30:27"/>Ukudunguluka ngaphakathi kwami kakukhawuli;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:27">insuku zokuhlupheka zingijamele.<verse eid="JOB 30:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 30:28"/>Ngihamba nje ngimnyama kubi, kungesikutshiswa lilanga;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:28">ngiyasukuma enkundleni ngicele uncedo.<verse eid="JOB 30:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOB 30:29"/>Sengingumfowabo wamakhanka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:29">umkhula wezikhova.<verse eid="JOB 30:29"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOB 30:30"/>Isikhumba sami siba mnyama, siyaxathuka;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:30">umzimba wami uyatshisa ngomkhuhlane.<verse eid="JOB 30:30"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOB 30:31"/>Ichacho lami selilungiselwe isililo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 30:31">lomqangala wami ulindele umkhosi wokukhala.”<verse eid="JOB 30:31"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="JOB 30"/>
  <chapter number="31" style="c" sid="JOB 31"/>
  <para style="s1">UJobe Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 31:1"/>“Ngasenza isivumelwano lamehlo ami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:1">ukuthi angakhangeli intombi ayihawukele.<verse eid="JOB 31:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 31:2"/>Siyini isabelo somuntu asabelwe nguNkulunkulu ophezulu na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:2">ilifa lakhe elivela kuSomandla phezulu?<verse eid="JOB 31:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 31:3"/>Akusikubhujiswa kwababi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:3">lokutshabalaliswa kwalabo abenza okubi na?<verse eid="JOB 31:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 31:4"/>Kanti kaziboni yini izindlela zami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:4">abale zonke izinyathelo zami?<verse eid="JOB 31:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 31:5"/>Nxa ngike ngahamba ngokwamanga</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:5">loba unyawo lwami lwakhuthalela inkohliso<verse eid="JOB 31:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 31:6"/>uNkulunkulu akangikale esikalini sakhe esiqotho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:6">ukuze abone ukuthi angilasici,<verse eid="JOB 31:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 31:7"/>nxa izinyathelo zami zike zaphambuka endleleni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:7">nxa inhliziyo yami ikhokhelwe ngamehlo ami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:7">noma kumbe izandla zami zike zangcoliswa,<verse eid="JOB 31:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 31:8"/>lapho-ke abanye kabazidlele lokho engikuhlanyeleyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:8">njalo amabele ami kawasitshunwe.<verse eid="JOB 31:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 31:9"/>Nxa inhliziyo yami ike yakhangwa ngowesifazane,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:9">kumbe nxa ngike ngacathama ngasemnyango kamakhelwane,<verse eid="JOB 31:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 31:10"/>lapho-ke owami umfazi kacholele enye indoda,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:10">njalo amanye amadoda kawalale laye.<verse eid="JOB 31:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 31:11"/>Ngoba lokho bekuzakuba lihlazo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:11">isono esifanele ukwahlulelwa.<verse eid="JOB 31:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 31:12"/>Kungumlilo otshisayo onguMaqothula;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:12">ngabe kwasiphuna isivuno sami.<verse eid="JOB 31:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 31:13"/>Nxa ngingaphathanga kuhle izisebenzi zami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:13">esesilisa lesesifazane</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:13">nxa kukhona abakusolayo kimi,<verse eid="JOB 31:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 31:14"/>ngizakuthini lapho uNkulunkulu esengibuza ngakho na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:14">Ngizaphendula ngithini nxa sekumele ngichaze na?<verse eid="JOB 31:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 31:15"/>Yena lowo owangenzayo esibelethweni kabenzanga labo na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:15">Kasuye yini yena kanye owasenzayo sonke</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:15">phakathi kwezisu zabomama na?<verse eid="JOB 31:15"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 31:16"/>Nxa ngilahlele eceleni izifiso zabayanga</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:16">loba ngayekela amehlo omfelokazi edinwa yizinyembezi,<verse eid="JOB 31:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 31:17"/>nxa ngizidlele ngedwa isinkwa sami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:17">ngingasabelani lezintandane,<verse eid="JOB 31:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 31:18"/>kodwa ebutsheni bami ngabondla njengaboyise,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:18">njalo kusukela ekuzalweni kwami ngamkhokhela umfelokazi,<verse eid="JOB 31:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 31:19"/>nxa ngike ngabona umuntu esifa ngokuswela izigqoko,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:19">loba umuntu oswelayo engelasivunulo,<verse eid="JOB 31:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 31:20"/>njalo inhliziyo yakhe ayingibusisanga</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:20">ngokumfudumeza ngoboya bezimvu zami,<verse eid="JOB 31:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 31:21"/>nxa ngike ngaphakamisa isandla sami phezu kwentandane,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:21">kodwa mina ngikwazi ukuthi bayangilalela emthethwandaba,<verse eid="JOB 31:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 31:22"/>nxa kunjalo kayikhumuke ingalo yami kusukela ehlombe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:22">kayephulwe endololwaneni.<verse eid="JOB 31:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 31:23"/>Ngoba ngesaba ukubhubhisa kukaNkulunkulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:23">kwathi ngokwesaba inkazimulo yakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:23">ngayekela ukwenza izinto ezinjalo.<verse eid="JOB 31:23"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 31:24"/>Nxa ngifake ithemba lami phezu kwegolide,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:24">loba ngathi kulo igolide elicolekileyo, ‘Ulithemba lami,’<verse eid="JOB 31:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 31:25"/>nxa bengithokoziswa yinotho yami enengi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:25">lenzuzo evele ngezandla zami,<verse eid="JOB 31:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 31:26"/>nxa ngilikhangele ilanga libenyezela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:26">loba inyanga ihamba ngenkazimulo,<verse eid="JOB 31:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 31:27"/>yaze yayengeka inhliziyo yami ngaphakathi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:27">nganga isandla sami ukuzikhonza,<verse eid="JOB 31:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 31:28"/>lezi lazo yizono ebezifanele ukwahlulelwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:28">ngoba bengizabe ngingathembekanga kuNkulunkulu ophezulu.<verse eid="JOB 31:28"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOB 31:29"/>Nxa ngike ngathokoza ngomnyama owehlele isitha sami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:29">kumbe ngagqabhaza ngohlupho olumehleleyo,<verse eid="JOB 31:29"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOB 31:30"/>kangivumelanga umlomo wami ukuba wenze isono</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:30">ngokuqalekisa ukuphila kwakhe,<verse eid="JOB 31:30"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOB 31:31"/>nxa abantu bendlu yami bengakaze bathi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:31">‘Ngubani ongazange azitike ngenyama kaJobe na?’<verse eid="JOB 31:31"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOB 31:32"/>kodwa kakulasihambi esake salala emgwaqweni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:32">ngoba umnyango wami wawuhlala uvulelwe izihambi<verse eid="JOB 31:32"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOB 31:33"/>nxa ngisithukuzile isono sami njengokwenziwa ngabantu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:33">ngokufihla umlandu wami enhliziyweni yami<verse eid="JOB 31:33"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="JOB 31:34"/>ngoba ngisesaba abantu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:34">ngithuthunyeliswa yikweyiswa ngabosendo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:34">ngazithulela ngaze ngala lokuphumela phandle.<verse eid="JOB 31:34"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="JOB 31:35"/>(Oh, kube ukhona ongizwayo!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:35">Sengisayina incwadi yokuzivikela kwami,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 31:35">uSomandla kangiphendule;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:35">ongimangalelayo kabhale phansi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:35">icala angethesa lona.<verse eid="JOB 31:35"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="JOB 31:36"/>Leyoncwadi ngingayithwala ehlombe lami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:36">ngingayithwala ekhanda njengomqhele.<verse eid="JOB 31:36"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="JOB 31:37"/>Bengingamchazela ngokugcweleyo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:37">ngazozonke izinyathelo zami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:37">ngisondele kuye njengenkosana.)<verse eid="JOB 31:37"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="JOB 31:38"/>Nxa ilizwe lakithi lingiphika</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:38">lemifolo yalo imanzi ngezinyembezi,<verse eid="JOB 31:38"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="JOB 31:39"/>nxa ngike ngadla izithelo zalo angaze ngabhadala</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:39">loba ngephula imimoya yabanikazi,<verse eid="JOB 31:39"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="JOB 31:40"/>nxa kunjalo kakumile ameva esikhundleni sengqoloyi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 31:40">lokhula esikhundleni sebhali.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="JOB 31:40">Aphela lapha amazwi kaJobe.<verse eid="JOB 31:40"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 31"/>
  <chapter number="32" style="c" sid="JOB 32"/>
  <para style="s1">Inkulumo Ka-Elihu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 32:1"/>Amadoda la womathathu ema ukuphendula uJobe ngoba wayelungile ngokubona kwakhe. <verse eid="JOB 32:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 32:2"/>Kodwa u-Elihu indodana kaBharakeli umBhuzi, owendlu kaRamu, wamzondela uJobe ngokuzigeza yena endaweni yokugezwa nguNkulunkulu. <verse eid="JOB 32:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 32:3"/>Wayebazondele njalo labangane labo bobathathu ngoba babengayitholanga indlela yokuphikisa uJobe kodwa bemlahlile ngokumsola. <verse eid="JOB 32:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 32:4"/>U-Elihu wayeke wema ukukhuluma loJobe ngoba babebadala kulaye. <verse eid="JOB 32:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 32:5"/>Kodwa kwathi esebona ukuthi wonke amadoda womathathu ayengaselalutho ayengalutsho, ulaka lwakhe lwavutha.<verse eid="JOB 32:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 32:6"/>Ngakho-ke u-Elihu indodana kaBharakeli umBhuzi wathi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 32:6">“Ngimncinyane ngeminyaka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:6">lina libadala;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 32:6">yikho bengisesaba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:6">ngithikaza ukutsho engikwaziyo.<verse eid="JOB 32:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 32:7"/>Ngikhumbule ngathi, ‘Kakukhulume ubudala;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:7">iminyaka yokukhula kayifundise ukuhlakanipha.’<verse eid="JOB 32:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 32:8"/>Kodwa kungumoya osemuntwini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:8">ukuphefumula kukaSomandla, okumupha ukuqedisisa.<verse eid="JOB 32:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 32:9"/>Kakusibo bodwa abadala abahlakaniphileyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:9">njalo kakusibo bodwa abalupheleyo abakuzwisisayo okulungileyo.<verse eid="JOB 32:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 32:10"/>Ngakho ngithi: Lalelani kimi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:10">lami ngizalitshela engikwaziyo.<verse eid="JOB 32:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 32:11"/>Bengithule lisakhuluma,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:11">ngikulalele ukucabanga kwenu;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 32:11">lathi lisadinga amazwi,<verse eid="JOB 32:11"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 32:12"/>ngalilalela ngokupheleleyo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 32:12">Kodwa kakho lamunye kini otshengise ukuthi uJobe ulahlekile;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:12">kakho omunye wenu osephendule imibono yakhe.<verse eid="JOB 32:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 32:13"/>Lingaze lathi, ‘Sesikutholile ukuhlakanipha;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:13">uNkulunkulu kaveze ukuphosisa kwakhe, hatshi umuntu.’<verse eid="JOB 32:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 32:14"/>Kodwa uJobe kakaqondisisi amazwi akhe kimi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:14">futhi kangiyikumphendula ngendlela yenu yokuphikisa.<verse eid="JOB 32:14"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 32:15"/>Sebededile kabaselakho okunye abangakutsho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:15">sebesilela amazwi.<verse eid="JOB 32:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 32:16"/>Ngike ngime na njengoba sebethule,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:16">sebemi nje laphayana bengaselampendulo?<verse eid="JOB 32:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 32:17"/>Lami ngisake ngikhulume;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:17">lami ngizakutsho engikwaziyo.<verse eid="JOB 32:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 32:18"/>Ngoba manengi amazwi engilawo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:18">umoya ongaphakathi kwami uyangifuqa;<verse eid="JOB 32:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 32:19"/>ngaphakathi ngiyafuthelana njengewayini elivalelwe embodleleni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:19">njengemixhaka yewayini esifuna ukudubuka.<verse eid="JOB 32:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 32:20"/>Kumele ngikhulume ukuze ngibhodle;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:20">kumele ngivule indebe zami ngiphendule.<verse eid="JOB 32:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 32:21"/>Kangizukutshengisa ubandlululo loba kukubani,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:21">futhi kangisoze ngiyenge muntu;<verse eid="JOB 32:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 32:22"/>ngoba ngabe ngangiligabazi ekukhulumeni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 32:22">uMenzi wami ubezangisusa masinyane.”<verse eid="JOB 32:22"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="JOB 32"/>
  <chapter number="33" style="c" sid="JOB 33"/>
  <para style="s1">U-Elihu Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 33:1"/>“Khathesi-ke, Jobe, lalela amazwi ami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:1">lalelisisa konke engikutshoyo.<verse eid="JOB 33:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 33:2"/>Sengizawuvula umlomo wami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:2">amazwi ami asesolimini lwami.<verse eid="JOB 33:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 33:3"/>Amazwi ami aphuma enhliziyweni eqotho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:3">izindebe zami zikhuluma ngokukholwa lokho engikwaziyo.<verse eid="JOB 33:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 33:4"/>UMoya kaNkulunkulu wangenza;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:4">umphefumulo kaSomandla ungipha impilo.<verse eid="JOB 33:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 33:5"/>Ngiphendula nxa usenelisa;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:5">zilungiselele ukuthi ungiphikise.<verse eid="JOB 33:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 33:6"/>Lami nginjengawe phambi kukaNkulunkulu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:6">lami njalo ngathathwa emhlabathini.<verse eid="JOB 33:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 33:7"/>Ukungesaba kwakho makungakwethusi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:7">njalo isandla sami masingasindi kuwe.<verse eid="JOB 33:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 33:8"/>Kodwa ukhulumile ngisizwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:8">ngiwezwile amazwi wona kanye,<verse eid="JOB 33:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 33:9"/>‘Ngimsulwa njalo kangilasono;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:9">ngihlanzekile kangilamlandu.<verse eid="JOB 33:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 33:10"/>Ikanti uNkulunkulu ubone okusolekayo kimi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:10">ungithatha njengesitha sakhe.<verse eid="JOB 33:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 33:11"/>Uyazikhina inyawo zami ngezibopho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:11">uyaziqaphelisisa zonke izindlela zami.’<verse eid="JOB 33:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 33:12"/>Kodwa ngiyakutshela ukuthi lapha uyalahleka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:12">uNkulunkulu mkhulu kulomuntu.<verse eid="JOB 33:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 33:13"/>Kungani umsola</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:13">usithi kaphenduli amazwi omuntu na?<verse eid="JOB 33:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 33:14"/>Ngempela uNkulunkulu uyakhuluma,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:14">khathesi akhulume ngale indlela,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 33:14">aphinde akhulume ngenye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:14">lokuba umuntu angaze akunanzelela.<verse eid="JOB 33:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 33:15"/>Kungaba ngephupho, kube ngombono ebusuku</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:15">lapho abantu belele befile</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:15">bethe nya emibhedeni yabo,<verse eid="JOB 33:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 33:16"/>angakhuluma ezindlebeni zabo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:16">abethuse ngezixwayiso,<verse eid="JOB 33:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 33:17"/>ukuze aguqule umuntu ekwenzeni okubi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:17">aqede ukuzikhukhumeza kwakhe,<verse eid="JOB 33:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 33:18"/>ukulondoloza umphefumulo wakhe ungayi egodini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:18">lempilo yakhe ingabhubhi ngenkemba.<verse eid="JOB 33:18"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 33:19"/>Loba umuntu angajeziswa ngobuhlungu esembhedeni wakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:19">langokuqaqamba okungathuliyo emathanjeni akhe,<verse eid="JOB 33:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 33:20"/>aze ezwe umzimba wakhe usunengwa yikudla</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:20">lomoya wakhe usenyanya lokudla okumnandi kakhulu.<verse eid="JOB 33:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 33:21"/>Inyama yakhe iyacikizeka iphele,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:21">lamathambo akhe ayekade evaliwe abonakale egcekeni.<verse eid="JOB 33:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 33:22"/>Umoya wakhe uyasondela egodini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:22">lempilo yakhe kuzo izithunywa zokufa.<verse eid="JOB 33:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 33:23"/>Kodwa nxa kulengilosi eceleni kwakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:23">engumeli, eyodwa phakathi kwenkulungwane,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:23">ukutshela umuntu okuyikho okumfaneleyo,<verse eid="JOB 33:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 33:24"/>ukuba lomusa kuye isithi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:24">‘Mxolele angayingena egodini;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:24">sengimzuzele inhlawulo yakhe yokumhlenga<verse eid="JOB 33:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 33:25"/>bese inyama yakhe ivuselelwa njengeyomntwana;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:25">iyavuselelwa ibe njengezinsukwini zobutsha bakhe.’<verse eid="JOB 33:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 33:26"/>Uyakhuleka kuNkulunkulu amthokozele,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:26">abubone ubuso bukaNkulunkulu amemeze ngentokozo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:26">uyabuyiselwa nguNkulunkulu esimeni sakhe sokulunga.<verse eid="JOB 33:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 33:27"/>Kuthi-ke abesebuya ebantwini athi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:27">‘Ngenza isono, ngahlanekela okulungileyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:27">kodwa kangisazuzanga obekungifanele.<verse eid="JOB 33:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 33:28"/>Wawuhlenga umphefumulo wami ukuze ungayi egodini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:28">ngakho ngizaphila ukuze ngikholise ukukhanya.’<verse eid="JOB 33:28"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOB 33:29"/>UNkulunkulu uyazenza zonke lezizinto emuntwini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:29">kabili, noma kathathu<verse eid="JOB 33:29"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOB 33:30"/>ukubuyisa umphefumulo wakhe ungayi egodini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:30">ukuthi isibane sokuphila sikhanye kuye.<verse eid="JOB 33:30"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOB 33:31"/>Nanzelela, Jobe, ulalele kimi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:31">thula kukhulume mina.<verse eid="JOB 33:31"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOB 33:32"/>Nxa ulolutho lokutsho, ngiphendula;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:32">khuluma sibili, ngoba ngifuna ukuthi ugezwe umlandu.<verse eid="JOB 33:32"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOB 33:33"/>Kodwa nxa lungekho lalela kimi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 33:33">thula zwi mina ngizakufundisa ukuhlakanipha.”<verse eid="JOB 33:33"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 33"/>
  <chapter number="34" style="c" sid="JOB 34"/>
  <para style="s1">U-Elihu Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 34:1"/>U-Elihu waqhubeka esithi:<verse eid="JOB 34:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 34:2"/>“Zwanini amazwi ami, lina madoda ahlakaniphileyo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:2">lalelani kimi, lina madoda ayizifundiswa.<verse eid="JOB 34:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 34:3"/>Phela indlebe iyawahlola amazwi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:3">njengolimi lunambitha ukudla.<verse eid="JOB 34:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 34:4"/>Asizihluzeleni thina okulungileyo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:4">kasifundeni ndawonye okuhle.<verse eid="JOB 34:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 34:5"/>UJobe uthi, ‘Kangilacala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:5">kodwa uNkulunkulu kangahluleli ngokulunga.<verse eid="JOB 34:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 34:6"/>Loba mina ngiqondile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:6">kuthiwa ngilamanga;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 34:6">loba ngingelacala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:6">umtshoko wakhe ungihlaba isilonda esingelaphekiyo.’<verse eid="JOB 34:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 34:7"/>UJobe kanti ungumuntu bani,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:7">onatha ukuklolodela njengamanzi?<verse eid="JOB 34:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 34:8"/>Uzwanana labantu abenza ububi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:8">uhambisana labantu ababi.<verse eid="JOB 34:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 34:9"/>Ngoba uthi, ‘Umuntu kakumsizi ngalutho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:9">ukuzama ukuthokozisa uNkulunkulu.’<verse eid="JOB 34:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 34:10"/>Ngakho lalelani kimi lina madoda azwisisayo.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:10">Kakube khatshana laye uNkulunkulu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:10">ukwenza ububi, khatshana kukaSomandla ukona.<verse eid="JOB 34:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 34:11"/>Uyamphindisela umuntu ngalokho akwenzileyo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:11">umehlisela lokho okufanele ukuziphatha kwakhe.<verse eid="JOB 34:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 34:12"/>Kakungeni engqondweni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:12">ukuthi uNkulunkulu angenza ububi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:12">ukuthi uSomandla</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:12">angakutshila ukwahlulela ngokulunga.<verse eid="JOB 34:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 34:13"/>Ngubani owambekayo phezu komhlaba na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:13">Ngubani owathi kalawule umhlaba wonke na?<verse eid="JOB 34:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 34:14"/>Aluba wayengathanda</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:14">asuse umoya wakhe lokuphefumula,<verse eid="JOB 34:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 34:15"/>bonke abantu babengatshabalala kanyekanye,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:15">umuntu wayezabuyela othulini.<verse eid="JOB 34:15"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 34:16"/>Nxa lilokuzwisisa, zwanini lokhu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:16">lalelani lokhu engikutshoyo.<verse eid="JOB 34:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 34:17"/>Kambe lowo ozonda ukwahlulela ngokulunga angabusa na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:17">Liyamlahla yini Yena oqotho njalo olamandla?<verse eid="JOB 34:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 34:18"/>Kayisuye yini othi emakhosini, ‘Kalisizi lutho,’</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:18">athi kwabayizikhulu, ‘Libabi,’<verse eid="JOB 34:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 34:19"/>ongatshengisi ukwazisa amakhosana kulabanye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:19">loba athande abanothileyo kulabayanga,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:19">ngoba bonke bangumsebenzi wezandla zakhe?<verse eid="JOB 34:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 34:20"/>Bayafa nje masinyane, loba phakathi kobusuku;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:20">abantu bayanyikinywa bedlule;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:20">abalamandla bayasuswa kungelasandla somuntu.<verse eid="JOB 34:20"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 34:21"/>Amehlo akhe aphezu kwezindlela zabantu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:21">ubona zonke izinyathelo zabo.<verse eid="JOB 34:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 34:22"/>Akulandawo emnyama loba ithunzi elisithileyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:22">lapho abenzi bobubi abangacatsha khona.<verse eid="JOB 34:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 34:23"/>UNkulunkulu kasweli ukuthi aphinde abahlolisise abantu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:23">ukuze abalethe ekwahlulelweni phambi kwakhe.<verse eid="JOB 34:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 34:24"/>Engaqalanga wahlola uyabaphahlaza abalamandla</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:24">abeke abanye endaweni yabo.<verse eid="JOB 34:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 34:25"/>Ngoba ezinanzelela izenzo zabo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:25">uyabagenqula ebusuku bahlifizeke.<verse eid="JOB 34:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 34:26"/>Uyabajezisa ngenxa yobubi babo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:26">kube segcekeni emuntwini wonke,<verse eid="JOB 34:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 34:27"/>ngoba baphambuka ekumlandeleni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:27">abaze banaka layiphi indlela yakhe.<verse eid="JOB 34:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 34:28"/>Benza ukukhala kwabayanga kweza phambi kwakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:28">laye wakuzwa ukukhala kwabasweleyo.<verse eid="JOB 34:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOB 34:29"/>Kodwa nxa elokhu ezithulele, ngubani ongamsola na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:29">Angafihla ubuso bakhe ngubani ongambona na?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 34:29">Kanti uphezu komuntu lesizwe ngokufanayo,<verse eid="JOB 34:29"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOB 34:30"/>ukwalela ongamesabiyo uNkulunkulu ukuthi abuse,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:30">ukuze angafakeli abantu izifu.<verse eid="JOB 34:30"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOB 34:31"/>Akesithi umuntu athi kuNkulunkulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:31">‘Ngilecala kodwa kangisayikona njalo.<verse eid="JOB 34:31"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOB 34:32"/>Ngifundisa lokho engingakuboniyo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:32">nxa ngenze okubi, kangisayikuphinda ngikwenze.’<verse eid="JOB 34:32"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOB 34:33"/>Pho uNkulunkulu akuvuze ngokwentando yakho na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:33">wena usala ukuphenduka?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 34:33">Kumele ukhethe wena, hatshi mina;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:33">ngakho ngitshela lokho okwaziyo.<verse eid="JOB 34:33"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="JOB 34:34"/>Amadoda alokuqedisisa azakutsho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:34">amadoda ahlakaniphileyo abangizwayo ngisithi kini,<verse eid="JOB 34:34"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="JOB 34:35"/>‘UJobe ukhuluma engelalwazi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:35">amazwi akhe kawalambono.’<verse eid="JOB 34:35"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="JOB 34:36"/>Oh, uJobe angasake alingwe ngokweqileyo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:36">ngoba uphendule njengomuntu omubi!<verse eid="JOB 34:36"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="JOB 34:37"/>Phezu kwesono sakhe wengeza ukuhlamuka;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:37">uyakloloda ngokuqakeza izandla zakhe phakathi kwethu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 34:37">andise amazwi akhe aphikisa uNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="JOB 34:37"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 34"/>
  <chapter number="35" style="c" sid="JOB 35"/>
  <para style="s1">U-Elihu Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 35:1"/>U-Elihu wasesithi:<verse eid="JOB 35:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 35:2"/>“Ukhumbula ukuthi lokhu kulungile yini?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:2">Uthi, ‘Ngizagezwa nguNkulunkulu.’<verse eid="JOB 35:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 35:3"/>Kodwa uyambuza uthi, ‘Kungisiza ngani lokhu na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:3">njalo ngizuzani ngokungenzi isono?’<verse eid="JOB 35:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 35:4"/>Ngithanda ukukuphendula</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:4">kanye labangane bakho abalapha.<verse eid="JOB 35:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 35:5"/>Ake ukhangele emazulwini ubone;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:5">khangela amayezi aphakeme kangaka ngaphezu kwakho.<verse eid="JOB 35:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 35:6"/>Ungaze wenze isono, lokho kumthinta ngani na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:6">Nxa izono zakho zizinengi, kwenzani lokho kuye na?<verse eid="JOB 35:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 35:7"/>Nxa ulungile, kuyini omnika khona wena na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:7">kumbe yena wamukelani esandleni sakho?<verse eid="JOB 35:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 35:8"/>Ububi bakho bulimaza kuphela umuntu onjengawe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:8">lokulunga kwakho kuthinta amadodana abantu kuphela.<verse eid="JOB 35:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 35:9"/>Abantu bayakhala ngomthwalo wokuncindezelwa;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:9">bacela ukuphunyuzwa ezingalweni zalabo abalamandla.<verse eid="JOB 35:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 35:10"/>Kodwa kakho othi, ‘Ungaphi uNkulunkulu uMenzi wami na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:10">opha amahubo ebusuku,<verse eid="JOB 35:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 35:11"/>osifundisayo thina kulezinyamazana zalapha emhlabeni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:11">asenze sihlakaniphe kulezinyoni zasemoyeni?’<verse eid="JOB 35:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 35:12"/>Kaphenduli nxa abantu bebiza</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:12">ngenxa yokuziphakamisa kwababi.<verse eid="JOB 35:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 35:13"/>Ngempela uNkulunkulu kakulaleli ukuncenga kwabo kwamanga;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:13">uSomandla kayilaleli into enjalo.<verse eid="JOB 35:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 35:14"/>Kuzakuba njani pho, angakulalela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:14">nxa usithi kawumboni,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 35:14">usithi indaba yakho iphambi kwakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:14">ngakho kuzamele ulinde yena,<verse eid="JOB 35:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 35:15"/>njalo futhi, ukuthi ulaka lwakhe kalujezisi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:15">njalo akabunanzi lakancane ububi.<verse eid="JOB 35:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 35:16"/>Yikho uJobe evula umlomo wakhe ekhuluma ize;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 35:16">ngokuswela ulwazi wandisa amazwi.”<verse eid="JOB 35:16"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 35"/>
  <chapter number="36" style="c" sid="JOB 36"/>
  <para style="s1">U-Elihu Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 36:1"/>U-Elihu waqhubeka esithi:<verse eid="JOB 36:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 36:2"/>“Ake lingibekezelele okwesikhatshana ukuze ngilitshengise</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:2">ukuthi kunengi okumele kutshiwo ngobuhle bukaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="JOB 36:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 36:3"/>Ngiluzuza kude ulwazi lwami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:3">ngithi ukwahlulela okulungileyo ngokukaMenzi wami.<verse eid="JOB 36:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 36:4"/>Yiba leqiniso ukuthi amazwi ami aqinisile;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:4">yena opheleleyo elwazini ulawe.<verse eid="JOB 36:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 36:5"/>UNkulunkulu ulamandla, kodwa keyisi muntu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:5">ulamandla njalo katshedi ezimisweni zakhe.<verse eid="JOB 36:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 36:6"/>Ababi kabayekeli bephila</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:6">kodwa abahluphekayo uyabapha okubafaneleyo.<verse eid="JOB 36:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 36:7"/>Kawasusi amehlo akhe kwabalungileyo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:7">ubakhweza esihlalweni kanye lamakhosi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:7">abaphakamise nini lanini.<verse eid="JOB 36:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 36:8"/>Kodwa nxa abantu bebotshwe ngamaketane,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:8">bethiwe nko ngezibopho zezinhlupheko,<verse eid="JOB 36:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 36:9"/>uyabatshela lokho abakwenzileyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:9">ukuthi benze isono ngokuziphakamisa.<verse eid="JOB 36:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 36:10"/>Ubenza balalele ukuqondiswa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:10">abalaye ukuthi baphenduke ebubini babo.<verse eid="JOB 36:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 36:11"/>Nxa bemlalela bamkhonze,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:11">zonke insuku zabo eziseleyo zizaphumelela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:11">leminyaka yabo ibe ngeyokusuthiseka.<verse eid="JOB 36:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 36:12"/>Kodwa nxa bengalaleli,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:12">bazabhubha ngenkemba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:12">bafe bengelalwazi.<verse eid="JOB 36:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 36:13"/>Abangamesabiyo uNkulunkulu bagodle ukusola enhliziyweni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:13">loba angaze ababophe kabaceli ukusizwa.<verse eid="JOB 36:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 36:14"/>Bafa besesebatsha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:14">bephakathi kweziphingi ezingamadoda,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:14">ezihlala ezindaweni zokukhonzela.<verse eid="JOB 36:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 36:15"/>Kodwa labo abahluphekayo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:15">uyabakhulula ekuhluphekeni kwabo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:15">ukhuluma labo besezinkathazweni zabo.<verse eid="JOB 36:15"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 36:16"/>Uyakulimukisa ukuthi uphume emihlathini yosizi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:16">uye endaweni ebanzi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 36:16">ekhululekileyo njalo engelazibopho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:16">ebumnandini betafula yakho igcwele izidlo ezimnandi.<verse eid="JOB 36:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 36:17"/>Kodwa manje usindwa yikwahlulelwa okulungele ababi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:17">ukuthonisiswa lokwahlulelwa ngokulunga</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:17">yikho osekukuduba.<verse eid="JOB 36:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 36:18"/>Qaphela kungabikhona okulingayo ngenotho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:18">ungavumeli ukuthengwa ngemali kukususe endleleni.<verse eid="JOB 36:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 36:19"/>Kambe inotho yakho loba konke ukutshikatshika kwakho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:19">kungakusekela ukuze ungangeni osizini na?<verse eid="JOB 36:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 36:20"/>Ungalangazeleli ubusuku,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:20">ukuze uyohudula abantu ezindaweni zabo.<verse eid="JOB 36:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 36:21"/>Qaphela ungangeni kokubi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:21">okukhanya ingathi uyakuthanda kulokuhlupheka.<verse eid="JOB 36:21"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 36:22"/>UNkulunkulu uphakeme ngamandla akhe.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:22">Ngubani ongafundisa njengaye na?<verse eid="JOB 36:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 36:23"/>Ngubani omisele izindlela zakhe na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:23">loba othe kuye, ‘Usuwenze okungalunganga?’<verse eid="JOB 36:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 36:24"/>Khumbula ukukhulisa umsebenzi wakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:24">abantu abawudumisileyo ngengoma.<verse eid="JOB 36:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 36:25"/>Bonke abantu jikelele bakubonile lokhu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:25">abantu bakukhangela bemi khatshana.<verse eid="JOB 36:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 36:26"/>Ubukhulu bukaNkulunkulu bungaphezulu kokuzwisisa kwethu!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:26">Iminyaka yakhe ingezake yaziwe.<verse eid="JOB 36:26"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 36:27"/>Uyawadonsa amathonsi amanzi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:27">aqulungane abe lizulu elingena ezifuleni;<verse eid="JOB 36:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 36:28"/>amayezi athulula amanzi awo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:28">kune izulu elikhulu ebantwini.<verse eid="JOB 36:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOB 36:29"/>Ngubani ongakuzwisisa ukuthi uwendlala njani amayezi na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:29">ukuthi ukhwaza njani esesiqongweni sakhe na?<verse eid="JOB 36:29"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOB 36:30"/>Ake libone ukuthi uwuhlakaza njani umbane wakhe azizingelezele ngawo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:30">abhukutshe ezinzikini zolwandle.<verse eid="JOB 36:30"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOB 36:31"/>Yiyo indlela abusa ngayo izizwe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:31">aziphe ukudla okunengi.<verse eid="JOB 36:31"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOB 36:32"/>Ugcwalisa izandla zakhe ngombane</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:32">awukhombise lapho omele utshaye khona.<verse eid="JOB 36:32"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOB 36:33"/>Ukuduma kwakhe kubika isiphepho esizayo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 36:33">lenkomo ziyatshengisa ukuza kwaso.”<verse eid="JOB 36:33"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="JOB 36"/>
  <chapter number="37" style="c" sid="JOB 37"/>
  <para style="s1">U-Elihu Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 37:1"/>“Konke lokhu kwenza inhliziyo yami itshaye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:1">ize itshede endaweni yayo.<verse eid="JOB 37:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 37:2"/>Lalela! Lalela ukubhonga kwelizwi lakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:2">ukuzamazama okuphuma emlonyeni wakhe.<verse eid="JOB 37:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 37:3"/>Uyawukhulula umbane wakhe ngaphansi kwawo wonke amazulu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:3">awuthumele emikhawulweni yomhlaba.<verse eid="JOB 37:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 37:4"/>Ngemva kwalokho kuza umdumo wokubhonga kwakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:4">uduma ngelizwi lakhe lobukhosi.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 37:4">Nxa ilizwi lakhe seliqaqamba</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:4">ulikhulula lonke angaligodli.<verse eid="JOB 37:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 37:5"/>Ilizwi likaNkulunkulu liduma ngezindlela ezimangalisayo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:5">wenza izinto ezinkulu ngaphezu kokuzwisisa kwethu.<verse eid="JOB 37:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 37:6"/>Utshela ungqwaqwane athi, ‘Khithika phezu komhlaba,’</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:6">lezulu athi kulo, ‘Thululeka ube yisihlambo esikhulu.’<verse eid="JOB 37:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 37:7"/>Ukuze kuthi bonke abantu abadalayo bakwazi ukusebenza kwakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:7">uyamisa umuntu wonke emsebenzini wakhe.<verse eid="JOB 37:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 37:8"/>Izinyamazana ziyacatsha;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:8">zihlale ezikhundleni zazo.<verse eid="JOB 37:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 37:9"/>Isiphepho siyaphuma ekamelweni laso,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:9">umqando uphume entshongolweni esikayo.<verse eid="JOB 37:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 37:10"/>Ukuphefumula kukaNkulunkulu kukhupha iliqhwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:10">amanzi aluwaca ajiye abe yilitshe.<verse eid="JOB 37:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 37:11"/>Ugcwalisa amayezi ngamanzi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:11">ahlakaze umbane wakhe ngawo.<verse eid="JOB 37:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 37:12"/>Ngokuqondisa kwakhe ayaqhela embese umhlaba wonke</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:12">ukuze enze loba yini awalaya yona.<verse eid="JOB 37:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 37:13"/>Uyawaletha amayezi ajezise ngawo abantu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:13">loba ukuthelezela umhlaba wakhe ukuze atshengise uthando lwakhe.<verse eid="JOB 37:13"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 37:14"/>Lalela lokhu, Jobe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:14">akume ukhumbule izimangaliso zikaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="JOB 37:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 37:15"/>Uyakwazi na ukuthi uNkulunkulu uwalawula njani amayezi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:15">enze umbane wakhe ulavuke?<verse eid="JOB 37:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 37:16"/>Uyakwazi na ukuthi amayezi emi njani elengile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:16">leyomimangaliso yakhe yena lowo opheleleyo elwazini?<verse eid="JOB 37:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 37:17"/>Wena oginqiswa yikutshisa kwezigqoko zakho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:17">nxa umhlaba uthule zwi kubetha umoya waseningizimu,<verse eid="JOB 37:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 37:18"/>ungamncedisa yini ukwendlala isibhakabhaka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:18">esilukhuni njengesibuko sensimbi yethusi?<verse eid="JOB 37:18"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 37:19"/>Ake usitshele ukuthi pho sithini kuye;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:19">ngeke siyimise kuhle indaba yethu ngoba kumnyama nje lapha kithi.<verse eid="JOB 37:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 37:20"/>Atshelwe kambe ukuthi ngifuna ukukhuluma?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:20">Ukhona umuntu ongacela ukuthi aginywe?<verse eid="JOB 37:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 37:21"/>Phela kakho ongalikhangela ilanga,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:21">njengoba licazimula kangaka esibhakabhakeni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:21">nxa umoya uwaphephule wonke amayezi kwacethula.<verse eid="JOB 37:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 37:22"/>Esuka enyakatho uqhamuka ngenkazimulo enjengegolide;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:22">uNkulunkulu uqhamuka ngobukhosi obesabekayo.<verse eid="JOB 37:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 37:23"/>USomandla asingeke simfinyelele njalo uphakeme ulamandla;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:23">ekwahluleleni kwakhe okuhle lokulunga okukhulu kancindezeli.<verse eid="JOB 37:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 37:24"/>Ngakho-ke abantu bayamhlonipha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 37:24">ngoba kanti kabanaki yini bonke abahlakaniphileyo enhliziyweni?”<verse eid="JOB 37:24"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 37"/>
  <chapter number="38" style="c" sid="JOB 38"/>
  <para style="s1">
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> Uyakhuluma</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 38:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasekhuluma loJobe ephakathi kwesiphepho. Wathi:<verse eid="JOB 38:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 38:2"/>“Ngubani na lowo odunga amacebo ami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:2">ngamazwi okungazi?<verse eid="JOB 38:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 38:3"/>Qina njengendoda;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:3">ngizakubuza,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:3">lawe uzangiphendula.<verse eid="JOB 38:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 38:4"/>Wawungaphi lapho ngibeka izisekelo zomhlaba na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:4">Ngitshela nxa uqedisisa.<verse eid="JOB 38:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 38:5"/>Ngubani owamisa izilinganiso zawo na? Phela angithi uyazi!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:5">Ngubani owayidonsayo intambo yokulinganisa kuwo na?<verse eid="JOB 38:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 38:6"/>Izinsika zawo zamiswa phezu kwani na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:6">loba ngubani owamisa ilitshe lawo lekhoneni na<verse eid="JOB 38:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 38:7"/>lapho izinkanyezi zokusa zazihlabelela kanyekanye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:7">lezingilosi zonke zamemeza ngentokozo?<verse eid="JOB 38:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 38:8"/>Ngubani owavalela ulwandle ngemva kwezivalo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:8">lapho selufohla esiswini na,<verse eid="JOB 38:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 38:9"/>lapho ngisenza amayezi aba yisembatho salo na</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:9">ngalugoqela ngomnyama omkhulu,<verse eid="JOB 38:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 38:10"/>lapho ngalubekela imikhawulo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:10">ngamisa iminyango yalo lemigoqo endaweni yayo,<verse eid="JOB 38:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 38:11"/>lapho engathi, ‘Ungeza uze ufike lapha kodwa ungedluli;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:11">kulapha amagagasi akho azigqajayo aphelela khona?’<verse eid="JOB 38:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 38:12"/>Sewake wabekela ikuseni umthetho na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:12">loba watshengisa ukusa indawo yakho<verse eid="JOB 38:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 38:13"/>ukuba kuphakamise umhlaba ngemiphetho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:13">kuthintithe ababi abakuwo?<verse eid="JOB 38:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 38:14"/>Umhlaba ubumbeka isimo njengebumba ufakwe uphawu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:14">imibala yawo ikhanye ithi bha njengelembu.<verse eid="JOB 38:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 38:15"/>Ababi bayacitshelwa ukukhanya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:15">lengalo yabo ephakanyisiweyo iyephulwa.<verse eid="JOB 38:15"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 38:16"/>Sewake wahamba emithonjeni yolwandle na</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:16">loba wahamba ezingoxweni zenziki yalo na?<verse eid="JOB 38:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 38:17"/>Amasango okufa aseke abonakaliswa kuwe na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:17">Usuke wawabona amasango ethunzi lokufa na?<verse eid="JOB 38:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 38:18"/>Ubuqedisisile na ubukhulu bobubanzi bomhlaba?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:18">Ngitshela nxa ukwazi konke lokhu.<verse eid="JOB 38:18"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 38:19"/>Yiphi indlela eya ekhaya elihlala ukukhanya na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:19">Ubumnyama bona buhlala ngaphi?<verse eid="JOB 38:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 38:20"/>Ungakusa ezindaweni zakho na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:20">Uyazazi izindlela eziya emizini yazo na?<verse eid="JOB 38:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 38:21"/>Ye uyakwazi, ngoba wawuvele usuzelwe!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:21">Usuphile iminyaka yonke le!<verse eid="JOB 38:21"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 38:22"/>Sewake wangena eziphaleni zikangqwaqwane</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:22">loba wabona iziphala zesiqhotho na,<verse eid="JOB 38:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 38:23"/>engizilindisele izikhathi zohlupho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:23">insuku zempi lokuhlasela na?<verse eid="JOB 38:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 38:24"/>Ingaphi indlela eya esigodlweni sokwaba umbane,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:24">loba indawo yokuhlakaza umoya wempumalanga phezu komhlaba na?<verse eid="JOB 38:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 38:25"/>Ngubani ogubhe intshukuntshu yezihlambo zezulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:25">lendlela yomdumo wesiphepho;<verse eid="JOB 38:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 38:26"/>ukuthelezela ilizwe elingahlali muntu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:26">inkangala okungelamuntu kuyo,<verse eid="JOB 38:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 38:27"/>ukusuthisa ilizwe elilugwadule</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:27">kulenze lihlume utshani na?<verse eid="JOB 38:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 38:28"/>Izulu elinayo liloyise na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:28">Ngubani onguyise wamathonsi amazolo na?<verse eid="JOB 38:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOB 38:29"/>Ngesikabani isisu esizala iliqhwa na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:29">Ngubani ozala umtshazo ovela phezulu na<verse eid="JOB 38:29"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOB 38:30"/>lapho amanzi abalukhuni njengelitshe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:30">lapho iphezulu yolwandle ijiyile?<verse eid="JOB 38:30"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOB 38:31"/>Ungasibopha na isiLimela lesi esihle?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:31">Ungazithukulula yini izintambo zeziNja?<verse eid="JOB 38:31"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOB 38:32"/>Ungawuletha na uMthala ngesikhathi sawo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:32">loba ukhuphe inkanyezi ethiwa yiNgulube lemidlwane yayo?<verse eid="JOB 38:32"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOB 38:33"/>Uyayazi imithetho yasezulwini na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:33">Ungawakha yini umbuso kaNkulunkulu emhlabeni?<verse eid="JOB 38:33"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="JOB 38:34"/>Ungawamemeza yini amayezi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:34">uthi akunethise ngesihlambo samanzi?<verse eid="JOB 38:34"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="JOB 38:35"/>Uyakuthuma yini ukuphazima kombane?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:35">Uyabika kuwe yini uthi, ‘Ngilapha’?<verse eid="JOB 38:35"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="JOB 38:36"/>Ngubani owapha inhliziyo ukuhlakanipha</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:36">kumbe owapha ingqondo ukuzwisisa na?<verse eid="JOB 38:36"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="JOB 38:37"/>Ngubani ololwazi lokubala amayezi na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:37">Ngubani ongagenqula amaqhaga asezulwini na<verse eid="JOB 38:37"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="JOB 38:38"/>nxa uthuli seluqina</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:38">lamagade omhlabathi esebumbene?<verse eid="JOB 38:38"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="JOB 38:39"/>Uyasizingelela na isilwanekazi ukudla kwaso,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:39">uyiqede indlala yezilwane<verse eid="JOB 38:39"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="JOB 38:40"/>lapho zilele ezikhundleni zazo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:40">kumbe zicwathile ezixukwini?<verse eid="JOB 38:40"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="JOB 38:41"/>Ngubani opha iwabayi ukudla</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:41">lapho amatsiyane alo ekhala kuNkulunkulu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 38:41">ezulazula ehayila ngendlala na?”<verse eid="JOB 38:41"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="JOB 38"/>
  <chapter number="39" style="c" sid="JOB 39"/>
  <para style="s1">
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 39:1"/>“Uyakwazi na ukuthi amagogo azala nini?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:1">Uyawubukele yini nxa impalakazi izala izinyane layo?<verse eid="JOB 39:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 39:2"/>Uyawuzibale yini izinyanga zize zizale?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:2">Uyasazi isikhathi ezizazala ngaso na?<verse eid="JOB 39:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 39:3"/>Ziyalala phansi zizale abantwana bazo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:3">kube sekuphela ubuhlungu bokuhelelwa kwazo.<verse eid="JOB 39:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 39:4"/>Amazinyane azo ayaqina akhule abe lamandla egangeni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:4">ayasuka ahambe angabuyi.<verse eid="JOB 39:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 39:5"/>Ngubani owakhulula ubabhemi weganga na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:5">Ngubani owathukulula igoda lakhe na?<verse eid="JOB 39:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 39:6"/>Ngamupha ugwadule lwaba likhaya lakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:6">lenkangala yetswayi ibe ngumango wakhe.<verse eid="JOB 39:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 39:7"/>Uyazincifela iziphithiphithi zedolobho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:7">kakuzwa ukukhahlanyezwa ngumtshayeli.<verse eid="JOB 39:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 39:8"/>Uyazihambela abhode izintaba emadlelweni akhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:8">edinga loba yini eluhlaza.<verse eid="JOB 39:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 39:9"/>Inyathi kambe izavuma ukukusebenzela na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:9">Izahlala esibayeni sakho ebusuku na?<verse eid="JOB 39:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 39:10"/>Ungayibamba ngomchilo ulime ngayo na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:10">Ingazilima na izigodi zakho?<verse eid="JOB 39:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 39:11"/>Ungayithemba yini ngenxa yamandla ayo amakhulu na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:11">Ungawuyekelela yona umsebenzi wakho onzima na?<verse eid="JOB 39:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 39:12"/>Ungayithemba ukuthi izalayitsha amabele akho na</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:12">iwase esizeni?<verse eid="JOB 39:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 39:13"/>Impiko zentshe zitshaya kakuhle,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:13">kodwa ngeke zilinganiswe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:13">lempiko kanye lezinsiba zengabuzane.<verse eid="JOB 39:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 39:14"/>Ibekela amaqanda ayo emhlabathini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:14">iwayekele afudumale etshebetshebeni,<verse eid="JOB 39:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 39:15"/>inganakananga ukuthi unyawo oluthile lungawahlifiza,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:15">ukuthi inyamazana yeganga ethile ingawanyathela.<verse eid="JOB 39:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 39:16"/>Amatsiyane ayo iyawakhahlameza, kube sengathi akusi wayo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:16">ingakhathali ukuthi ukubekela kwayo kwaba yize,<verse eid="JOB 39:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 39:17"/>ngoba uNkulunkulu kayiphanga ukuhlakanipha</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:17">loba ingqondo yokubona okufaneleyo.<verse eid="JOB 39:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 39:18"/>Kodwa nxa isiselula impiko zayo ukuthi igijime,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:18">iyalihleka ibhiza lomgadi walo.<verse eid="JOB 39:18"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 39:19"/>Uyalipha na wena ibhiza amandla</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:19">kumbe ugqokise intamo yalo ngomhlonga na?<verse eid="JOB 39:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 39:20"/>Uyalenza leqe njengentethe na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:20">lingethuse ngokuhwabha kwalo kokuziqenya?<verse eid="JOB 39:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 39:21"/>Liyaphanda ngenkani, lithokoziswa ngamandla alo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:21">lidlubulunde lihlasela isitha.<verse eid="JOB 39:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 39:22"/>Liyakuhleka ukwesaba, kalesabi lutho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:22">kaliyikhekhelezi inkemba.<verse eid="JOB 39:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 39:23"/>Umxhaka wemitshoko ukhehlezela emhlubulweni walo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:23">ndawonye lomkhonto obenyezelayo kanye lomdikadika.<verse eid="JOB 39:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 39:24"/>Liyafuthelana ngamadlabuzane ligijime limbe phansi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:24">kakulivumeli ukuma nxa icilongo selikhala.<verse eid="JOB 39:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 39:25"/>Konela ukuthi likhale icilongo lihwabhe lithi, ‘Aha!’</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:25">Lihle lilizwe iphunga lempi isesekhatshana,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:25">ukukhwaza kwezinduna lomkhosi wempi.<verse eid="JOB 39:25"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 39:26"/>Ukhozi luphatshiswa yikuhlakanipha kwakho na</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:26">lwelule impiko zalo ziqonde eningizimu?<verse eid="JOB 39:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 39:27"/>Ukhozi luntweza ngokutshelwa nguwe yini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:27">kanye lokwakhela isidleke salo esiqongweni?<verse eid="JOB 39:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 39:28"/>Luhlala eliweni, lulale khona ebusuku;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:28">idwala elililiwa yilo inqaba yalo.<verse eid="JOB 39:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOB 39:29"/>Ludinga ukudla kwayo lusuka khona;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:29">amehlo alo akubona ekude.<verse eid="JOB 39:29"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOB 39:30"/>Amatsiyane alo azitika ngegazi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 39:30">kuthi lapho okulokubuleweyo khona lalo lukhona.”<verse eid="JOB 39:30"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 39"/>
  <chapter number="40" style="c" sid="JOB 40"/>
  <para style="s1">
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 40:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuJobe:<verse eid="JOB 40:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 40:2"/>“Lowo ophikisana loSomandla angamqondisa na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:2">Yena lowo obeka uNkulunkulu icala kamphendule!”<verse eid="JOB 40:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 40:3"/>Ngakho uJobe wasephendula <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wathi:<verse eid="JOB 40:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 40:4"/>“Kakungilingananga, ngingakuphendula njani na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:4">Ngivala umlomo wami ngesandla sami.<verse eid="JOB 40:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 40:5"/>Ngikhulumile kanye, kodwa kangilampendulo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:5">kabili, kodwa kangisayikukhuluma njalo.”<verse eid="JOB 40:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 40:6"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasekhuluma loJobe ephakathi kwesiphepho wathi:<verse eid="JOB 40:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 40:7"/>“Qina njengendoda;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:7">ngizakubuza,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:7">wena uzangiphendula.<verse eid="JOB 40:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 40:8"/>Ungakusola na ukwahlulela kwami ngokulunga?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:8">Ungangilahla ukuze uzigeze na?<verse eid="JOB 40:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 40:9"/>Ulayo ingalo enjengekaNkulunkulu na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:9">njalo ilizwi lakho lingaduma njengelakhe yini?<verse eid="JOB 40:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 40:10"/>Nxa kunjalo zicecise ngobukhosi langenkazimulo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:10">uzembathise ngodumo lobukhosi.<verse eid="JOB 40:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 40:11"/>Khulula ukuvutha kolaka lwakho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:11">khangela wonke umuntu ozigqajayo umthobise,<verse eid="JOB 40:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 40:12"/>khangela wonke umuntu ozigqajayo umbeke phansi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:12">ubacobodise ababi khonapho abakhona.<verse eid="JOB 40:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 40:13"/>Bambele bonke ndawonye othulini;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:13">goqela ubuso babo engcwabeni.<verse eid="JOB 40:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 40:14"/>Lapho-ke lami ngizavuma kuwe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:14">ukuthi isandla sakho sokunene singakusindisa.<verse eid="JOB 40:14"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 40:15"/>Khangela imvubu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:15">engayidala kanye lawe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:15">njalo edla utshani njengenkomo.<verse eid="JOB 40:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 40:16"/>Ilamandla amangalisayo okhalweni lwayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:16">amandla angaka emisipheni yesisu sayo!<verse eid="JOB 40:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 40:17"/>Umsila wayo uyazunguza njengomsedari;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:17">imisipha yemilenze yayo yalukene.<verse eid="JOB 40:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 40:18"/>Amathambo ayo alezimbobo zethusi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:18">lezitho zayo zinjengemiqwayi yensimbi.<verse eid="JOB 40:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 40:19"/>Iyingqala yezidalwa zikaNkulunkulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:19">kodwa uMenzi wayo angayehlula ngenkemba yakhe.<verse eid="JOB 40:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 40:20"/>Izintaba zimlethela izithelo zazo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:20">kuthi zonke izilo zeganga zidlalele eduze.<verse eid="JOB 40:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 40:21"/>Ilala ngaphansi kwezihlahla ezibukekayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:21">isithekile phakathi kwemihlanga exhaphozini.<verse eid="JOB 40:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 40:22"/>Izihlahla ezinhle ziyayisitha ngemithunzi yazo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:22">imidubu okhunjini lomfula iyihonqolozele.<verse eid="JOB 40:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 40:23"/>Nxa umfula uthwele izikhukhula kayethuki;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:23">kayithi thiki lokuba iJodani ithululela impophoma emlonyeni wayo.<verse eid="JOB 40:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 40:24"/>Ukhona yini ongayibamba ngamehlo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 40:24">kumbe ayithiye ayibhoboze amakhala na?”<verse eid="JOB 40:24"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="JOB 40"/>
  <chapter number="41" style="c" sid="JOB 41"/>
  <para style="s1">
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> Uqhubeka Ekhuluma</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 41:1"/>“Ungambamba na uLeviyathani ngewuka</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:1">loba uhitshele ulimi lwakhe ngentambo na?<verse eid="JOB 41:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 41:2"/>Ungawufaka umkhala yini emakhaleni akhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:2">kumbe ubhoboze umhlathi wakhe ngewuka na?<verse eid="JOB 41:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 41:3"/>Uzabe elokhu ekuncenga yini ukuthi umzwele?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:3">Uzakhuluma lawe ngamazwi apholileyo yini?<verse eid="JOB 41:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 41:4"/>Uzakwenza isivumelwano lawe na</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:4">ukuthi abe yisichaka sakho kokuphela?<verse eid="JOB 41:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 41:5"/>Ungamenza abe yisifuyo sokudlalisa njengenyoni na</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:5">kumbe umfake umkhungo adlaliswe ngamantombazana na?<verse eid="JOB 41:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 41:6"/>Abathengi bazabhejelana ngentengo yakhe na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:6">Bazakwahlukaniselana ngaye na abathengi?<verse eid="JOB 41:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 41:7"/>Ungasibhoboza yini isikhumba sakhe ngenhlendla</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:7">loba ikhanda lakhe ngemikhonto yokuciba inhlanzi?<verse eid="JOB 41:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 41:8"/>Ungabeka isandla phezu kwakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:8">uzahlala ukukhumbula ukutshukana kwenu ungaphindi futhi!<verse eid="JOB 41:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 41:9"/>Ukucabanga ukuthi ungamehlula kuyize;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:9">ukumbona nje kodwa kuqeda amandla.<verse eid="JOB 41:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 41:10"/>Kakho ongaba lesibindi sokuthi alwe laye.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:10">Pho ngubani ongamelana lami na?<verse eid="JOB 41:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 41:11"/>Ngubani engilomlandu kuye othi kangihlawule na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:11">Konke okukhona ngaphansi kwezulu ngokwami.<verse eid="JOB 41:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 41:12"/>Kangisoze ngikhawule ukubabaza izitho zakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:12">amandla akhe langesimo sakhe esihle.<verse eid="JOB 41:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 41:13"/>Ngubani ongaxebula isikhumba sakhe na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:13">Ngubani ongasondela kuye ngamatomu na?<verse eid="JOB 41:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 41:14"/>Ngubani ongaqunga isibindi avule iminyango yomlomo wakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:14">ogqagqelwe zingavula zamazinyo na?<verse eid="JOB 41:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 41:15"/>Umhlane wakhe ulezinhlu zamahawu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:15">abophene silikici;<verse eid="JOB 41:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 41:16"/>yilelo lithe mba kwelinye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:16">okuthi kakungeni moya phakathi kwawo.<verse eid="JOB 41:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 41:17"/>Anamathelene ndawonye;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:17">abambene okokuthi angeke ehlukaniswe.<verse eid="JOB 41:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 41:18"/>Ukuthimula kwakhe kukhupha inhlansi zomlilo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:18">amehlo akhe anjengemisebe yokusa.<verse eid="JOB 41:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 41:19"/>Amalangabi omlilo alavuka emlonyeni wakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:19">inhlansi zomlilo ziqhatsha ziphuma khona.<verse eid="JOB 41:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 41:20"/>Intuthu ithunqa iphuma emakhaleni akhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:20">kungathi isuka embizeni ebilayo phezu komlilo wemihlanga.<verse eid="JOB 41:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOB 41:21"/>Ukuphefumula kwakhe kulumathisa amalahle,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:21">njalo kulavuka amalangabi emlonyeni wakhe.<verse eid="JOB 41:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 41:22"/>Amandla akhe asentanyeni yakhe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:22">okuphambi kwakhe kuhle kuphele amandla.<verse eid="JOB 41:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOB 41:23"/>Amavinqo enyama yakhe abambene nki;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:23">aqine nko kawehlukaniseki.<verse eid="JOB 41:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 41:24"/>Isifuba sakhe silukhuni njengelitshe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:24">siqine njengengaphansi kwembokodo.<verse eid="JOB 41:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 41:25"/>Uthi nxa ephakama kwesabe amaqhawe ngokwawo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:25">atshede ebalekela ukubhula komsila wakhe.<verse eid="JOB 41:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOB 41:26"/>Inkemba leyo emfikelayo kayenzi lutho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:26">kumbe umkhonto, loba umtshoko loba isijula.<verse eid="JOB 41:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOB 41:27"/>Insimbi uyithatha njengotshani</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:27">lethusi kungathi luluthi olubolileyo.<verse eid="JOB 41:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOB 41:28"/>Imitshoko kayimenzi abaleke;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:28">lamatshe esavutha anjengomule kuye.<verse eid="JOB 41:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOB 41:29"/>Induku kuye ingumuca wotshani;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:29">uyahleka esizwa ukukhenceza komdikadika.<verse eid="JOB 41:29"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOB 41:30"/>Ingaphansi yomzimba wakhe injengendengezi ezibukhali,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:30">itshiya umzila odakeni kungathi yisileyi esizunguzekayo.<verse eid="JOB 41:30"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOB 41:31"/>Udunga inziki zamanzi ayabuke njengembiza enkulu ibila,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:31">aluvube ulwandle njengembiza yamagcobo.<verse eid="JOB 41:31"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOB 41:32"/>Ngemva kwakhe utshiya umzila okhazimulayo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:32">umuntu angazathi ulwandle luloboya obumhlophe.<verse eid="JOB 41:32"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOB 41:33"/>Kakukho emhlabeni okulingana laye,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:33">isidalwa esingesabiyo.<verse eid="JOB 41:33"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="JOB 41:34"/>Ubakhangelela phansi bonke abathi bazithembile;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 41:34">uyinkosi phezu kwabo bonke abazigqajayo.”<verse eid="JOB 41:34"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 41"/>
  <chapter number="42" style="c" sid="JOB 42"/>
  <para style="s1">UJobe Uyaphendula</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOB 42:1"/>UJobe wasemphendula <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wathi:<verse eid="JOB 42:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 42:2"/>“Ngiyazi ukuthi ungazenza zonke izinto;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 42:2">kalikho icebo lakho elingavinjwa.<verse eid="JOB 42:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOB 42:3"/>Ubuzile wathi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 42:3">‘Ngubani lo ovala iseluleko sami engelalwazi na?’</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOB 42:3">Ngeqiniso ngikhulumile ngezinto ebengingazizwisisi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 42:3">izinto ezimangalisayo engingeke ngizazi.<verse eid="JOB 42:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 42:4"/>Wena uthe, ‘Lalela manje, mina ngizakhuluma;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 42:4">ngizakubuza,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 42:4">wena uzangiphendula.’<verse eid="JOB 42:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOB 42:5"/>Indlebe zami zasezizwile ngawe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 42:5">kodwa manje amehlo ami asekubonile.<verse eid="JOB 42:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 42:6"/>Ngakho sengizeyisa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 42:6">sengiphenduka ngizilahla othulini lasemlotheni.”<verse eid="JOB 42:6"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isiphetho Sendaba</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 42:7"/>Kwathi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> esetshilo lezizinto kuJobe wathi ku-Elifazi umThemani, “Ngikuzondele wena kanye labangane bakho bobabili, ngoba kalikhulumanga ngami okulungileyo njengenceku yami uJobe. <verse eid="JOB 42:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOB 42:8"/>Ngakho manje thathani inkunzi eziyisikhombisa lenqama eziyisikhombisa liye encekwini yami uJobe liyekwenza umnikelo wenu wokutshiswa. Inceku yami uJobe izalikhulekela, mina ngizawamukela umkhuleko wayo ngingaze ngalijezisa okufanele ubuthutha benu. Kalikhulumanga ngami okulungileyo njengenceku yami uJobe.” <verse eid="JOB 42:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOB 42:9"/>Ngakho u-Elifazi umThemani, uBhilidadi umShuhi loZofari umNahama benza lokho abakutshelwa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>; njalo <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wawemukela umkhuleko kaJobe.<verse eid="JOB 42:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOB 42:10"/>UJobe esebakhulekele abangane bakhe, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wamenza waphumelela njalo wamupha okunengi okuphindwe kabili kulokho ayelakho kuqala. <verse eid="JOB 42:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 42:11"/>Bonke abafowabo labodadewabo kanye lobani owayemazi ngaphambili weza ukuzakudla laye endlini yakhe. Bamkhalela, bamzwela ngakho konke ukuhlupheka <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ayemehlisele khona, kwathi ngulowo lalowo wamupha ulutho lwesiliva kanye lesongo legolide.<verse eid="JOB 42:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 42:12"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wayibusisa impilo yokucina kaJobe ukwedlula eyokuqala. Waba lezimvu eziyizinkulungwane ezilitshumi lane, izinkulungwane eziyisithupha zamakamela, inkulungwane yezipani zenkabi labobabhemi abayinkulungwane. <verse eid="JOB 42:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 42:13"/>Waphinda njalo waba lamadodana ayisikhombisa lamadodakazi amathathu. <verse eid="JOB 42:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 42:14"/>Indodakazi yokuqala wayetha ibizo elithi Jemima, eyesibili yayinguKheziya, eyesithathu yaba nguKhereni-Haphutshi. <verse eid="JOB 42:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOB 42:15"/>Kakuzange kube khona elizweni lonke abesifazane ababebahle njengamadodakazi kaJobe, njalo uyise wawabela ilifa kanye labanewabo.<verse eid="JOB 42:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOB 42:16"/>Ngemva kwalokhu uJobe waphila iminyaka elikhulu lamatshumi amane; wababona abantwabakhe labantwababo kwaze kwaba yisizukulwane sesine. <verse eid="JOB 42:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 42:17"/>UJobe wafa esemdala njalo eseluphele.<verse eid="JOB 42:17"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOB 42"/>
</usx>
